(100, 'Karne', 'Karne', 478, 'akrne138', 'akrne138en', 'Ekscentrični i nadasve orginalni mješoviti band narodnog imena Karne je postao zaštitini znak Sarajevo Rock Fest. Obzirom da ne nastupaju tako često, zapravo prije bi se reklo da nastupaju vrlo, vrlo rijetko ovo je odlična prilika i povod da ih vidite i uživo čujete. Fedja i ekipa zasigurno znaju napraviti štimung...', 'The eccentric and highly original mixed band of folk names Karne has become a trademark of Sarajevo Rock Fest. Since it does not occur so often, in fact It is more likely to perform very, very rarely this is an excellent opportunity and reason to see them and hear live. Fedja and the team certainly know how to make atmosphere ...', '/look/events/8885_karne1.jpg', '+387 61 48 19 25', '2016-08-13 23:00:00', 4, 'marketing@infinity.ba', 1, 0, 1),
