(102, 'Summer Disco Selection', 'Summer Disco Selection', 1644, 'summer28', 'summer28en', '<p>Summer Disco Selection\n</p><p>\nKoncept AQUARIUS SARAJEVO pokrenut je davne 1999. na Grbavici tik uz stadion (zgrada LORIS) u želji prezentiranja stečenog ugostiteljskog znanja te iskustva kako u predratnom Sarajevu tako i u inostranstvu. Nakon prvih 6 godina rada,2005. AQUARIUS seli u naselje Šoping u veći i ekskluzivniji prostor u kojem se i sada nalazi. U vječitoj želji za razvojem i profesonalnim usavršavanjem 2007. nastaje firma ZARMED d.o.o. koja se svojim kvalitetom i konstantnim poslovnim napredovanjem, Sarajlijama i gostima Grada, uspijeva nametnuti kao respektabilna firma za ugostiteljstvo i usluge. </p>', '<p>Summer Disco Selection\n</p><p>\nThe concept of Aquarius SARAJEVO was launched back in 1999 in Grbavica next to the stadium (building LORIS) in an effort to present the acquired knowledge and experience of catering to the pre-war Sarajevo and abroad. After the first 6 years of operation, the 2005th Aquarius moves to the village shopping in larger and more exclusive area in which it is situated now. In the eternal desire to develop and 2007. This professional training company formed armed Ltd. that their quality and constant business advancement, the people of Sarajevo and guests of the city, manages to impose such a respectable company for catering and services.</p>', '/look/events/6694_aquarius.jpg', '+387 61 210 788', '2016-08-02 21:00:00', 4, 'aquariussarajevo@gmail.com', 1, 0, 1),
