(104, 'Unplugged Plug', 'Unplugged Plug', 478, 'unplug168', 'unplug168en', '<p>Unplugged plug je band koji postoji već nekih 15-tak godina i koji iza sebe ima preko 1000 većinom klupskih nastupa, te se svrstava u red najboljih klupskih BiH bandova.</p><p>Aktualnu postavu banda čine:</p><p>-Salih Hadžiabdić – vokal, ritam gitara</p><p>-Adi Isaković – bas, prateći vokal</p><p>-Denis Amitović – solo gitara</p><p>-Bruno Misanović – klavijature, prateći vokal</p><p>-Jasmin Efendić – bubnjevi, udaraljke</p><p>Članovi banda su iskusni muzičari koji su se profilirali u raznim bandovima, prolazili kroz razne sviračke i autorske faze i žanrove, i surađivali sa mnogobrojnim BiH muzičarima i autorima.</p>', '<p></p><p>Unplugged plug is a band that has been around for some 15 years and who has had a more than 1,000 mostly club performances, and ranks among the best club bands BiH.</p><p>The current lineup consists of the band:</p><p>Sal Spencer - vocals, rhythm guitar</p><p>-Adi Isakovic - bass, backing vocals</p><p>-Denis Amitović - guitar</p><p>-Bruno Misanovic - keyboards, backing vocals</p><p>-Jasmin Efendic - drums, percussion</p><p>Members of the band are experienced musicians who were profiled in various bands, went through various music-playing and authoring phase and genres, and collaborated with numerous BiH musicians and authors.</p><p></p>', '/look/events/2320_unplug.jpg', '+387 61 48 19 25', '2016-08-16 23:00:00', 4, 'marketing@infinity.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(105, 'Činčila', 'Činčila', 478, 'cincila178', 'cincila178en', '<p>Činčila je autorski psihodelični funk-rock bend osnovan 2012. godine u Sarajevu. Grupa izvlači kreativnu energiju iz zajedničkog dugogodišnjeg druženja, divljanja, glupiranja i maštanja. Bend pored muzike uključuje elemente likovne umjetnosti, performansa i kostimografije. Pored toga, bend Činčila je sigurno prvi bend na ovim prostorima koji počinje da kombinuje funk-rock sa psihodelijom i likovnim vizuelnim elementima, uključujući performans i scenski nastup.</p>', '<p>Činčila is the author psychedelic funk-rock band formed in 2012 in Sarajevo. The group draws creative energy from a common long-time friendship, wild, clowning and fantasies. The band next to the music incorporates elements of visual art, performance art and costume design. In addition, the band Chinchilla is certainly the first band in this region that begins to combine funk-rock with psychedelic art and visual elements, including performance and stage performance.</p>', '/look/events/8775_cinicila.jpg', '+387 61 48 19 25', '2016-08-17 23:00:00', 4, 'marketing@infinity.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(106, 'Erogene Zone', 'Erogene Zone', 478, 'zone188', 'zone188en', '<p>Grupa Erogene Zone osnovana je u Sarajevu krajem 1992. godine.Tokom ratnih godina nastupaju po sarajevskim klubovima. Ljeta&nbsp;1994 godine. objavljuju debi album Šuti seko šuti kojeg je nemoguće nabaviti jer je štampan u samo 500 primjeraka i nije bio u javnoj prodaji. Te godine od Studio 99 dobili su nagradu Fenix u konkurenciji najboljeg rock albuma. Drugi album grupa je objavila krajem 1997.godine pod nazivom Robija i na njemu se nalazi 12 pjesama. Sredinom 1999 godine. objavili su svoj treći album XXL za koji su dobili odlične kritike i koji se smatra njihovim najzrelijim djelom. Njihov četvrti album završen je početkom 2003. godine i nosi naziv Mistični znaci. Moderan pristup i dobra svirka čine ih onim što oni jesu. Prva znacajnija priznanja stizu pozivom iz Italije i nastupima na koncertu u Skandiciju, a 17. maja 1996.</p>', '<p>Band Erogene Zone was established in Sarajevo in late 1992 godine.Tokom war years perform at Sarajevo clubs. Summers & nbsp; 1994. released debut album Shut seco silent which is impossible to obtain because it is printed in only 500 copies and was not sold to the public. That year of Studio 99 received an award in the competition Fenix best rock album. The second album the group released in late 1997 under the name of Robbie and therein lies the 12 songs. In the middle of 1999. released their third album, XXL for which they received rave reviews and is considered their most mature work. Their fourth album was completed in early 2003 and bears the name of mystical signs. Modern approach and good music make them what they are. First significant recognition call comes from Italy and performances at the concert in skandic and 17 May in 1996. </p>', '/look/events/7044_zone.jpg', '+387 61 48 19 25', '2016-08-18 23:00:00', 4, 'marketing@infinity.ba', 1, 0, 1),
