(140, 'Mahnitost', 'Frenzy', 100, 'mahnitost168', 'mahnitost168en', '<p>Mahnitost\r\n</p><p>\r\nIstanbul se bori s političkim nasiljem. Visokopozicionirani policijski oficir Hamza nudi Kadiru uslovno puštanje iz zatvora. Uslov za puštanje na slobodu je da Hamza pristane raditi za novu obavještajnu jedinicu sastavljenu od sakupljača smeća. Kadir prihvata ponudu i počinje skupljati smeće u oronulim naseljima kako bi u otpadu tražio materijale preostale nakon kućne izrade eksplozivnih naprava. U jednom od oronulih naselja, Kadir nalazi svoga mlađeg brata Ahmeta.</p>', '<p>Frenzy\r\n</p><p>\r\nIstanbul is struggling with political violence. A high-ranking police officer Hamza offers Kadir conditional release from prison. The condition for release is that Hamza agrees to work for a new intelligence unit composed of the garbage collector. Kadir accepts the offer and begins to collect garbage in dilapidated neighborhoods in order to waste looking for materials remaining after a homemade explosive device. In one of the dilapidated village, Kadir is her younger brother Ahmet.</p>', '/look/events/5153_mahnitost.jpg', '+387 33 221 516', '2016-08-16 16:00:00', 1, 'info-sff@sff.ba', 1, 1, 0),
(141, 'Matura', 'Graduation', 100, 'matura158', 'matura158en', '<p>Matura\r\n</p><p>\r\nDoktor Romeo Aldea, nastanjen u planinskom gradiću u Transilvaniji, svoju je kćerku Elizu odgajao s idejom da će kada napuni 18 godina napustiti porodični dom kako bi živjela i studirala u inostranstvu. Njegov plan bi se uskoro trebao ostvariti; Eliza je dobila stipendiju za studij psihologije u Velikoj Britaniji.</p>', '<p>Graduation\r\n</p><p>\r\nDoctor Romeo Aldea, housed in a mountain town in Transylvania, their daughter Eliza was raised with the idea that when the age of 18 to leave the family home to living and studying abroad. His plan would soon be achieved; Eliza was awarded a scholarship to study psychology in the UK.</p>', '/look/events/8918_matura.jpg', '+387 33 221 516', '2016-08-15 16:00:00', 1, 'info-sff@sff.ba', 1, 1, 0),
(142, 'Noćni život ', 'Nightlife', 100, 'noćni138', 'noćni138en', '<p>Noćni život \r\n</p><p>\r\nPoznati advokat jedne je noći pronađen na trotoaru uz glavnu ulicu u centru Ljubljane. Jedva da je svjestan, leži u lokvi krvi i tijelo mu je prekriveno psećim ugrizima. Doktori se u bolnici bore za njegov život dok se njegova šokirana žena mora suočiti sa svojim najdubljim strahovima. Tokom te noći, ona će prekršiti sva moralna pravila za koja se čitav život zalagala. Ovo je film o društvu u kojem je strah pokretačka snaga. </p>', '<p>Nightlife\r\n</p><p>\r\nThe famous lawyer one night found on the sidewalk along the main street in the center of Ljubljana. He barely conscious, lying in a pool of blood, and his body was covered in dog bites. Doctors in the hospital fighting for his life while his shocked wife must face their deepest fears. During the night, it will break all the moral precepts of which is a lifetime advocate. This is a film about a society where fear is the driving force.</p>', '/look/events/4634_nzivot.jpg', '+387 33 221 516', '2016-08-13 16:00:00', 1, 'info-sff@sff.ba', 1, 1, 0),
(144, 'Prekid', 'Interruption', 100, 'prekid178', 'prekid178en', '<p>Prekid\n</p><p>\nU pozorištu u centru Atine igra se postmoderna teatarska adaptacija jedne klasične grčke tragedije. Kao i svake večeri, publika zauzima mjesta i predstava počinje. Odjednom, svjetla na pozornici se gase. Na scenu se penje grupa naoružanih mladih ljudi obučenih u crno. Izvinjavaju se za prekid i pozivaju publiku da im se pridruži na sceni. Publika je zbunjena, još uvijek im nije jasno da li je ovaj prekid dio predstave ili nije. Predstava se nastavlja, samo što sada život imitira umjetnost umjesto da umjetnost imitira život.</p>', '<p>Interruption\n</p><p>\nIn the theater in central Athens game postmodern theatrical adaptation of one of the classic Greek tragedy. As every evening, the audience takes place and play begins. Suddenly, the lights go out on stage. At the scene trailing a group of armed young men dressed in black. We apologize for the disruption and invite the audience to join them on stage. The audience is confused, they are still not clear whether the termination part of the show or not. The play continues, only now does life imitate art rather than art imitates life.</p>', '/look/events/4426_prekid.jpg', '+387 33 221 516', '2016-08-17 16:00:00', 1, 'info-sff@sff.ba', 1, 1, 0),
(145, 'Sieranevada', 'Sieranevada', 100, 'sieranevada198', 'sieranevada198en', '<p>Sieranevada\n</p><p>\nTri dana nakon napada na redakciju satiričnog magazina Charlie Hebdo u Parizu i četrdeset dana nakon smrti njegovog oca, četrdesetogodišnji doktor Lary provodi subotu u Bukureštu na porodičnom okupljanju u čast preminuloga. Okupljanje ne protiče po planu, okupljeni žustro raspravljaju i na površinu izbijaju dijametralno suprotna mišljenja. Prisiljen da se sukobi sa svojim strahovima i prošlošću i da preispita svoje mjesto u porodici, Lary ima samo jedan izbor - da obznani istinu.</p>', '<p>Sieranevada\n</p><p>\nThree days after the attack on the satirical magazine Charlie Hebdo in Paris and forty days after the death of his father, forty years Dr. Lary carried out Saturday in Bucharest at a family gathering in honor of the deceased. Gathering no runs according to plan, gathered heated argument and resurface diametrically opposed views. Forced to conflicts with their fears and past and to question her place in the family, Lary has only one choice - to make known the truth.</p>', '/look/events/5012_siera.jpg', '+387 33 221 516', '2016-08-19 16:00:00', 1, 'info-sff@sff.ba', 1, 1, 0),
(146, 'Smrt u Sarajevu', 'Death in Sarajevo', 1145, 'smrt178', 'smrt178en', '<p>Smrt u Sarajevu\r\n</p><p>\r\nSarajevo, 28. juni 2014. godine. U hotelu Europa, najboljem hotelu u gradu, direktor Omer sprema se da dočeka delegaciju istaknutih diplomata. Na stotu godišnjicu atentata, koji se smatra povodom Prvog svjetskog rata, iz Sarajeva bi se trebao poslati poziv na mir i razumijevanje u svijetu. Ali osoblje hotela muče druge brige. Nakon što mjesecima nisu dobili plate, oni planiraju stupiti u štrajk. Istovremeno, u izolovanom predsjedničkom apartmanu, gost iz Francuske uvježbava svoj govor. </p>', '<p>Death in Sarajevo\r\n</p><p>\r\nSarajevo, 28 June 2014. The hotel Europa, the best hotel in town, Director Omer awaits the arrival of a delegation of prominent diplomats. On the hundredth anniversary of the assassination, which is considered on the occasion of the First World War, in Sarajevo should send a call for peace and understanding in the world. But hotel staff plague other concerns. After months have not been paid, they plan to go on strike. At the same time, isolated in the presidential suite, a guest from France rehearsing his speech.</p>', '/look/events/3606_smrtss.jpg', '+387 33 221 516', '2016-08-17 20:00:00', 1, 'info-sff@sff.ba', 1, 1, 0),
