(207, 'Čudovištance Molly', 'Monster Molly', 1145, 'molly148', 'molly148en', '<p>Čudovištance Molly\r\n</p><p>\r\nČudovište Molly jedva čeka da se beba čudovište izlegne iz jajeta. Na kraju krajeva, nikada nije imala maloga brata ili sestru s kojima bi se mogla maziti i igrati. Ali Mollyni roditelji prvo moraju otići na ostrvo s jajima kako bi sačekali da se prinova izlegne. Na tom se ostrvu rađaju sva čudovišta. Otkrivši da su roditelji zaboravili ponijeti njen poklon za bebu, Molly brzo kreće za njima...</p>', '<p>Monster Molly\r\n</p><p>\r\nMonster Molly can not wait to have a baby monster hatches from an egg. After all, never had a little brother or sister with whom to be able to cuddle and play. But Molly''s parents must first go to the island with eggs to wait for the acquisition hatches. At this island give birth to all the monsters. Having discovered that the parents forgot to bring her a gift for the baby, Molly is moving quickly for them ...</p>', '/look/events/33_moli.jpg', '+387 33 221 516', '2016-08-14 12:15:00', 1, 'info-sff@sff.ba', 1, 1, 0),
(208, 'Dedo: Mehmet u žutim čizmama', 'Dede: Mehmet with the yellow boots', 1145, 'mehmet188', 'mehmet188en', '<p>Dedo: Mehmet u žutim čizmama\r\n</p><p>\r\nDEDE je topla filmska priča o potrazi jedanaestogodišnje djevojčice Merel za njenim biološkim dedom Turčinom. Tokom svoje potrage, Merel upada u smiješne i teške situacije i upoznaje zanimljive, čudne likove koji će doprinijeti njenom ličnom razvoju. </p>', '<p>Dede: Mehmet with the yellow boots\r\n</p><p>\r\nDEDE is a warm film story about the search eleven girls Merel for her biological grandfather Turk. During his quest, Merel decline in funny and difficult situations and meets interesting and strange characters who will contribute to their personal development.</p>', '/look/events/1599_dedo.jpg', '+387 33 221 516', '2016-08-18 18:00:00', 1, 'info-sff@sff.ba', 1, 1, 0),
(209, 'Dobro provedeno poslijepodne', 'A well spent afternoon', 1145, 'dobro168', 'dobro168en', '<p>Dobro provedeno poslijepodne\r\n</p><p>\r\nNakon još jednog u nizu neuspješnih intervjua za posao, otac provodi poslijepodne sa svojim sedmogodišnjim sinom. Slučajno pronalaze novčanik pun novca i otac sinu pokazuje šta su prave životne vrijednosti i kako ispravno postupiti.</p>', '<p>A well spent afternoon\r\n</p><p>\r\nAfter another in a series of unsuccessful job interviews, the father spends the afternoon with her seven-year son. I accidentally found a wallet full of money and his son shows what the true values, and to do the right thing.</p>', '/look/events/8466_dobro.jpg', '+387 33 221 516', '2016-08-18 18:00:00', 1, 'info-sff@sff.ba', 1, 1, 0),
(210, 'Gospođica Nemoguća', 'Miss Impossible', 1145, 'gospođica148', 'gospođica148en', '<p>Gospođica Nemoguća\r\n</p><p>\r\nNekima bi se Aurorin život mogao učiniti dosadnim. Ali, kada ste trinaestogodišnja djevojčica sa nepomirljivim stavovima o dječacima, školi, porodici i prijateljima, vaš život može djelovati kao razdragana psihodrama.</p>', '<p>Miss Impossible\r\n</p><p>\r\nSome would be Aurora''s life could not do boring. But when you''re a girl of thirteen with the irreconcilable positions of the boys, school, family and friends, your life can act as a cheerful psychodrama.</p>', '/look/events/5028_nemog.jpg', '+387 33 221 516', '2016-08-14 18:00:00', 1, 'info-sff@sff.ba', 1, 1, 0),
(213, 'Hevisauri', 'Heavysaurs', 1145, 'hevisauri168', 'hevisauri168en', '<p>Hevisauri\r\n</p><p>\r\nTokom posjete zabavnom parku sa školom, desetogodišnji Toni i njegova drugarica iz razreda Suvi otkrivaju Hevisaure, stvorenja slična dinosaurima koja zanimaju samo hrana i rock’n’roll. Hevisauri su društveni, zabavni i znaju kako zavladati scenom, ali zarobljenici su bešćutnog biznismena Maxima koji ih želi iskoristiti za svoje poslovne planove. Suvi i Toni moraju pokrenuti zajedničku borbu kako bi spasili muzikalne Hevisaure. </p>', '<p>Heavysaurs\r\n</p><p>\r\nDuring a visit to an amusement park with a school, a ten-year Toni and his classmate Dry reveal Hevisaure, creatures like dinosaurs that are only interested in food and rock''n''roll. Hevisauri are social, fun and know how to dominate the scene, but the prisoners were callous businessman Maxima who wants to exploit them for their business plans. Dry and Toni have to start a common struggle to save the musical Hevisaure.</p>', '/look/events/5810_hevis.jpg', '+387 33 221 516', '2016-08-16 18:00:00', 1, 'info-sff@sff.ba', 1, 1, 0),
(214, 'Moj prijatelj Raffi', 'My Friend Raffi', 1145, 'moj178', 'moj178en', '<p>Moj prijatelj Raffi\r\n</p><p>\r\nZlatni hrčak Raffi je kućni ljubimac osmogodišnjeg Sammija. Mali glodar je po svemu poseban. Ne samo da može zabijati golove loptom već može i nanjušiti krijumčarenu robu i to bolje od psa tragača. Raffi se jednoga dana iznenada razboljeva i ispada da je bolest ozbiljnija nego što se mislilo: ima srčano oboljenje koje zahtijeva operaciju. Loša situacija postaje još gora kada Raffi iznenadno nestaje!</p>', '<p>My Friend Raffi\r\n</p><p>\r\nGolden Hamster Raffi''s pet eight years Sammy. A small rodent is all special. Not only can score goals ball already can smell the contraband and the better of the bloodhound. Raffi one day suddenly falls ill and it turns out that the disease is more serious than previously thought: there are heart disease that requires surgery. A bad situation gets worse when Raffi suddenly disappears!</p>', '/look/events/9806_prijat.jpg', '+387 33 221 516', '2016-08-17 18:00:00', 1, 'info-sff@sff.ba', 1, 1, 0),
(215, 'Moj život kao Tikvica ', 'My life as a Zucchini', 1145, 'tikvica138', 'tikvica138en', '<p>Moj život kao Tikvica \r\n</p><p>\r\nFilm prati sudbinu desetogodišnjeg dječaka, poznatog pod nadimkom Tikvica, koji nakon majčine smrti završava u sirotištu. Pratimo dječaka dok prevazilazi prepreke kako bi se uklopio u novu sredinu okružen malom grupom djece s kojom se, kao i s njim, život grubo poigrao. </p>', '<p>My life as a Zucchini\r\n</p><p>\r\nThe film follows the fate of the ten year old boy, whose nickname flask, who after her mother''s death ends up in an orphanage. We follow the boys, while overcoming obstacles in order to fit the new environment surrounded by a small group of children who, like him, living rough challenged.</p>', '', '+387 33 221 516', '2016-08-13 18:00:00', 1, 'info-sff@sff.ba', 1, 1, 0),
(218, 'Nina', 'Nina', 1145, 'nina188', 'nina188en', '<p>Nina \r\n</p><p>\r\nŠestogodišnja Nina igra se sa svojim starijim bratom na morskoj plaži. Brat uskoro napušta sestru kako bi se igrao s jednim dječakom. Nakon što je ostavljena sama, Nina odlučuje otići s plaže i uputiti se u šetnju uz stijenje.</p>', '<p>Nina\r\n</p><p>\r\nThe six-year Nina plays with his older brother on the sea beach. Brother soon leaves a sister to play with one child. After being left alone, Nina decides to go to the beach and set off for a walk along the cliffs.</p>', '', '+387 33 221 516', '2016-08-18 18:00:00', 1, 'info-sff@sff.ba', 1, 1, 0),
(219, 'Novajlija', 'The New Kid', 1145, 'novajlija198', 'novajlija198en', '<p>Novajlija\r\n</p><p>\r\nPrva Benoitova sedmica u novoj školi ne protiče po planu. Popularna djeca okupljena u Charlesovoj bandi ga neprijateljski tretiraju, a samo su ga štreberi, koliko-toliko, ljubazno dočekali. Srećom, u školi upoznaje Johannu, lijepu djevojčicu iz Švedske s kojom će se sprijateljiti i u koju će se zaljubiti. Međutim, ona postepeno postaje sve bliža Charlesovoj bandi. Po savjetu svoga ujaka, Benoit organizuje zabavu na koju poziva svu djecu iz razreda. To mu je prilika da postane popularan i ponovo pridobije Johannu. </p>', '<p>The New Kid\r\n</p><p>\r\nBenoit first week of the new school is not flowing as planned. Popular children gathered in Charles''s gang by hostile treated, and only by nerds, more or less, kindly welcomed. Fortunately, the school meets Johanna, a beautiful girl from Sweden with which to make friends and to you will fall in love. However, it gradually becomes closer to Charles''s gang. On the advice of his uncle, Benoit organize the party that invites all children in class. It''s his chance to become popular and win again Johann.</p>', '', '+387 33 221 516', '2016-08-19 18:00:00', 1, 'info-sff@sff.ba', 1, 1, 1),
(220, 'OFFLINE - da li si spreman za sljedeći nivo?', 'OFFLINE - Are You Ready for the Next Level?', 1145, 'offline208', 'offline208en', '<p>OFFLINE - da li si spreman za sljedeći nivo?\r\n</p><p>\r\nSedamnaestogodišnji gejmer Jan većinu vremena provodi na kompjuteru u ulozi hrabrog ratnika Fenrisa. Dok se priprema za skorašnji online turnir Ragnarök, iznenada biva izbačen iz igre. U panici shvata da ga je hakirao drugi igrač, Loki. Ne samo da je ostao bez internet konekcije već mu ni mobilni telefon ni debitna kartica ne rade. </p>', '<p>OFFLINE - Are You Ready for the Next Level?\r\n</p><p>\r\nSeventeen year old gamer Jan most of the time on the computer in the role of a brave warrior Fenris. While preparing for the upcoming online tournament Ragnarök, is suddenly thrown out of the game. In a panic realize that it was hacked by another player, Loki. Not only was left without an internet connection but it is not a cell phone is not a debit card does not work.</p>', '', '+387 33 221 516', '2016-08-20 18:00:00', 1, 'info-sff@sff.ba', 1, 1, 1),
