(253, 'Jason Bourne', 'Jason Bourne', 1145, 'jason1117', 'jason1117en', '<p>Matt Damon se vraća svojoj najpoznatijoj ulozi Jasona Bournea. Paul Greengrass, redatelj „Bournove nadmoći“ i „Bournovog ultimatuma“, ponovo se pridružuje Damonu i režira novi nastavak Bournove franšize, u kojem će nekadašnji najsmrtonosniji operativac CIA izaći iz sjenke.\r\n</p><h2>MATT DAMON JE JASON BOURNE</h2><p><strong>Originalni naslov:</strong>&nbsp;Jason Bourne</p><p><strong>Redatelj:</strong>&nbsp;Paul Greengrass &nbsp;</p><p><strong>Uloge:</strong>&nbsp;Matt Damon, Alicia Vikander, Vincent Cassel...</p><p><strong>Žanr:</strong>&nbsp;Akcija, triler</p><p><strong>Trajanje:</strong>&nbsp;123 min</p>', 'The film starts with a brief recap of David Webb (Matt Damon) when he first joined Treadstone, going into his training to become an assassin and into his new life as the Jason Bourne. After exposing Blackbriar (in ''the Bourne Ultimatum''), Bourne has been hiding out in Greece for the past eight years. He engages in hand-to-hand combat with other men. One man he takes on gets knocked out in one punch.\r\n<br>\r\nMATT DAMON JE JASON BOURNE\r\nOriginalni naslov: Jason Bourne\r\nRedatelj: Paul Greengrass \r\nUloge: Matt Damon, Alicia Vikander, Vincent Cassel...\r\nŽanr: Akcija, triler\r\nTrajanje: 123 min', '/look/events/9257_jamson.jpg', '+387 33 567 230', '2016-08-11 17:30:00', 1, 'info@cinemacity.ba', 1, 0, 0),
