(1122, 'Majstor i Margarita', 'The Master and Margarita', 3881, 'majstor111', 'majstor111en', '<p>\r\n\r\nMajstor i Margarita je roman Mikhaila Bulgakova, napisan između 1928 i 1940, ali neobjavljen u formi knjige do 1967. godine.\r\n\r\nMnogi kritičari ga smatraju jednim od najboljih romana 20-tog stoljeća i jednom od najboljih sovjetskih satira. \r\n\r\nU romanu, đavo posjećuje ateistični Sovjetski Savez, pod maskom dobro odjevenog gospodina koji se predstavlja kao Wolland, profesor crne magije.\r\n\r\n</P>', '<p>\r\n\r\nThe Master and Margarita is a novel by Mikhail Bulgakov, written between 1928 and 1940, but unpublished in book form until 1967.\r\n\r\nMany critics consider it to be one of the best novels of the 20th century, as well as the foremost of Soviet satires.\r\n\r\nIn the novel, the devil pays a visit to the officially atheist Soviet Union, appearing as a well-dressed but somehow foreign-looking gentleman who introduces himself as Wolland, professor of black magic.\r\n\r\n</P>', '', '033 664 070', '2016-11-02 20:00:00', 3, 'teatarsartr@yahoo.com', 1, 0, 1),
