(1228, 'SREDNJA ŠKOLA: NAJGORE RAZDOBLJE MOG ŽIVOTA', 'Middle School: The Worst Years of My Life ', 1145, 'sskola', 'sskolaen', '<p>Priča prati život Rafea Khatchadoriana koji i bez problema u srednjoj školi ima dovoljno problema kod kuće. Srećom, napravio je plan za najbolju godinu u povijesti. Sa svojim najboljim prijateljem Leonardom, Rafe će pokušati prekršiti baš svako pravilo ponašanja u njihovoj školi...<br></p>', '<p>Imaginative quiet teenager Rafe Katchadorian is tired of his middle school''s obsession with the rules at the expense of any and all creativity. Desperate to shake things up, Rafe and his best friends have come up with a plan: break every single rule in the school and let the students run wild.<br></p>', '/look/events/4625_mskul.jpg', '+387 33 567 230', '2016-11-04 16:10:00', 1, 'info@cinemacity.ba', 1, 0, 0),
