(1259, 'Skroz - Svirka uživo', 'Skroz - Live', 478, 'skroz1111', 'skroz1111en', '<p>Skroz - Svirka uživo\r\n</p><p>\r\nBend Skroz nastao je 1996. godine i jedan je od najboljih i najpopularnijih bendova na lokalnoj i regionalnoj pop - rock sceni. </p>\r\n', '<p>Skroz - Live\r\n</p><p>\r\nBend Skroz created in 1996 and is one of the best and most popular bands on the local and regional pop - rock scene.</p>\r\n', '', ' 387 61 502 476', '2016-11-11 22:30:00', 4, '', 1, 0, 1),
(1260, 'Julije Cezar', 'Julius Caesar', 100, 'julije2911', 'julije2911en', '<p>Julije Cezar\n</p><p>\nPišući o ubistvu Julija Cezara u rimskom senatu, ustvari, ispisuje tužnu priču o krahu plemenitih revolucionarnih htjenja, koja se, u sudaru sa ličnim interesima, vlastoljublju i pohlepom samih revolucionara, pretvaraju u svoju nakaradnu suprotnost. \nJunaci antičkog Rima, postaju, petnaest vijekova kasnije, Shakespearovi savremenici, uronjeni u spletke i zavere elizabetanskog dvora, ali i savremenici našeg historijskog trenutka u kome je moguće posljednje decenije naše aktuelne istorije posmatrati kroz prizmu likova i odnosa Julija Cezara. </p>\n', '<p>Julije Cezar\r\n</p><p>\r\nWriting about the murder of Julius Caesar in the Roman Senate, in fact, print the sad story about the collapse of noble revolutionary aspirations, that is, in a clash with personal interests, love of power and greed themselves revolutionaries, turn into their opposite, ugly.\r\nThe heroes of ancient Rome, becoming, fifteen centuries later, Shakespeare''s contemporaries, immersed in intrigue and conspiracy Elizabethan court, but also contemporaries of our historical moment in which it is possible the last decade of our current history viewed through the prism of the characters and the relationships of Julius Caesar. </p>\r\n', '', ' 387 33 226 431', '2016-11-29 19:30:00', 3, 'info@nps.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1261, 'Julije Cezar', 'Julius Caesar', 100, 'julije3011', 'julije3011en', '<p>Julije Cezar\r\n</p><p>\r\nPišući o ubistvu Julija Cezara u rimskom senatu, ustvari, ispisuje tužnu priču o krahu plemenitih revolucionarnih htjenja, koja se, u sudaru sa ličnim interesima, vlastoljublju i pohlepom samih revolucionara, pretvaraju u svoju nakaradnu suprotnost. \r\nJunaci antičkog Rima, postaju, petnaest vijekova kasnije, Shakespearovi savremenici, uronjeni u spletke i zavere elizabetanskog dvora, ali i savremenici našeg historijskog trenutka u kome je moguće posljednje decenije naše aktuelne istorije posmatrati kroz prizmu likova i odnosa Julija Cezara. </p>\r\n', '<p>Julije Cezar\r\n</p><p>\r\nWriting about the murder of Julius Caesar in the Roman Senate, in fact, print the sad story about the collapse of noble revolutionary aspirations, that is, in a clash with personal interests, love of power and greed themselves revolutionaries, turn into their opposite, ugly.\r\nThe heroes of ancient Rome, becoming, fifteen centuries later, Shakespeare''s contemporaries, immersed in intrigue and conspiracy Elizabethan court, but also contemporaries of our historical moment in which it is possible the last decade of our current history viewed through the prism of the characters and the relationships of Julius Caesar. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 226 431', '2016-11-30 19:30:00', 3, 'info@nps.ba', 1, 0, 1),
