(1269, 'Kad bi naglas govorili', 'If we speak out loud', 305, 'govorili711', 'govorili711en', '<p>Kad bi naglas govorili\r\n</p><p>\r\nOva predstava se bavi likovima koje svakodnevno srećemo u haustorima, ispred zgrade, pored zgrade, svuda oko nas. Oni možda imaju iste probleme kao i mi, ali to nikad nećemo saznati jer smo prestali otvoreno pričati. Da, mi žučno pričamo o vremenu, politici, velikim temama – ali negdje u tim velikim temama smo se izgubili mi, mali ljudi. Mali ljudi sa nama velikim problemima. A, potrebno je samo malo hrabrosti, malo spremnosti da podijelimo pokoju emociju, intimu, sa ljudima oko nas, kako bi shvatili da svuda oko nas postoje osjećajna, ranjiva bića koja imaju iste probleme. Ljudska bića spremna i sposobna da nam pomognu, da nas usreće, da budu naši idealni partneri. </p>\r\n', '<p>If we speak out loud\r\n</p><p>\r\nThis play deals with the characters that we meet every day in the hallways, in front of the building, next to the building, all around us. They may have the same problems as we do, but it''ll never know because we stopped to talk openly. Yes, we are learning about the weather, politics, big issues - or somewhere in these big issues we''re lost, little people. Small people with us a lot of trouble. And, it only takes a little courage, a little willingness to share the odd emotion, intimacy, with the people around us, to realize that all around us there are sensitive, vulnerable beings who have the same problems. Human beings willing and able to help us, to make us happy, to be our ideal partners. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 550 475', '2016-11-07 20:00:00', 3, 'info@kamerniteatar55.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1270, 'Tamburaši - Orkestar Artis', 'Tamburaši - Orkestar Artis', 1632, 'tamburasi711', 'tamburasi711en', '<p>Tamburaši - Orkestar Artis\r\n</p><p>\r\nHistorija, tradicija i kvalitet na jednom mjestu, najbolje opisuju jedinstveni ugostiteljski objekat u Sarajevu – Pivnicu HS. Nalazi se u Centru Sarajeva, u dijelu Starog Grada na Bistriku, samo nekoliko metara od Sarajevske pivare, u zgradi koja je zaštićeni historijski objekt. Pored Pivnice HS nalazi se jedini muzej pivarstva u BiH. </p>\r\n', '<p>Tamburaši - Orkestar Artis\r\n</p><p>\r\nHistory, tradition and quality in one place, best describe the unique restaurant in Sarajevo - Pub HS. It is located in the center of Sarajevo, in part of the Old City in Bistrik, just a few meters from Sarajevo Brewery, in a building that is a protected historic building. In addition to the pub HS is the only brewery museum in BiH. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 239 740', '2016-11-07 21:00:00', 4, 'pivnica.hs@pivara.ba', 1, 0, 1),
