(1305, 'Crvenkapica na tačke naopačke', 'Little Red wheelbarrow upside down', 3882, 'crvenkapica1111', 'crvenkapica1111en', '<p> Crvenkapica na tačke naopačke\r\n</p><p>\r\nČetvero prijatelja Elma, Mario, Sanin i Damir jednog dosadnog poslijepodneva odluče da ožive bajku Crvenkapica na tavanu Marijevog stana.  U igri Crvenkapica sazna za plan zle Vještice i Vuka da opljačkaju zimnicu njene bake i tada se, svi njeni prijatelji iz Začarane šume koristeći se trikovima iz ovih igara, ujedinjuju da osujete Vješticu i Vuka u čemu naravno i uspjevaju.</p>\r\n', '<p> Little Red wheelbarrow upside down\r\n</p><p>\r\nThe four friends, Elma, Mario, Sanin and Damir one boring afternoon, decide to revive the fairy tale Little Red Riding Hood in the attic of Mario''s apartment. In the game Little Red Riding Hood finds out about the plan and the Evil Witch and Wolf to loot food for the winter of her grandmother and then, all her friends from the Enchanted Forest using the tricks of these games in order to thwart the Witch and Vuk what course and succeeding.</p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 442 572 ', '2016-11-11 18:30:00', 3, 'pozmladi@bih.net.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1306, 'Kokoška', 'Kokoška', 3882, 'kokoska1611', 'kokoska1611en', '<p>Kokoška\n\n</p><p>\nDanas kada je upravo naš svakodnevni život postao najprodavaniji medijski materijal, ova predstava, na jedan ironično-komičan način govori o životu ljudi kojima teatarska umjetnost predstavlja osnovni uslov egzistencije. </p>\n', '<p>Kokoška\n</p><p>\nToday when exactly our daily lives has become the best-selling media material, this performance, one ironically-humorous way about the life of people who theatrical art is a basic condition of existence. </p>\n', '', ' +387 33 442 572 ', '2016-11-16 20:00:00', 3, 'pozmladi@bih.net.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1307, 'Vremenski tunel', 'The Time tunnel', 3882, 'vremenski2211', 'vremenski2211en', '<p>Vremenski tunel\r\n</p><p>\r\n Tri studenta (dva mladića i djevojka) ulaze u Bosansku piramidu sunca, tražeći dokaze koji će potvrditi ili pobiti teoriju o Bosni kao kolijevci civilizacije. Tako počinje njihovo putovanje kroz vrijeme i istoriju Bosne i Hercegovine.</p>\r\n', '<p>The Time tunnel\n</p><p>\n Three students (two men and a girl) venture into the Bosnian Pyramid of the Sun,searching for evidence to confirm or refute the theory that Bosnia is the cradle of civilization. And so begins their journey through time and history of Bosnia and Herzegovina.</p>\n', '', '+387 33 442 572 ', '2016-11-22 20:00:00', 3, 'pozmladi@bih.net.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1315, 'Abeceda', 'Alphabet', 3882, 'abeceda2711', 'abeceda2711en', '<p>Abeceda\r\n</p><p>\r\nPredstava Abeceda, nastala je po tekstu Feride Duraković, a praizvedba je bila davne i ratne 1995. Odlučili smo se za obnovu zatop što je Abeceda namjenski pravljena za predškolski uzrast i naše prvačiće – publiku prema koja je do sada bila zanemarena, a upravo prema najmlađima imamo i najveću odgovornost. </p>\r\n', '<p>Alphabet\n</p><p>\nThe play Alphabet, was created after the text Ferida Durakovic, a premiere was back in the war of 1995 We decided to rebuild atop the Alphabet dedicated made for preschool children and our first-grade pupils - the audience towards which so far has been ignored, and just the youngest we have the greatest responsibility. </p>', '', '+387 33 442 572 ', '2016-11-27 11:00:00', 3, 'pozmladi@bih.net.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1316, 'Njuškalo', 'Sniffer', 3882, 'njuskalo2911', 'njuskalo2911en', '<p>Njuškalo\r\n</p><p>\r\nNjuškalo, jedan od najizvođenijih komada Anthony Schaffera, koji je doživio i nekoliko tv i filmskih adaptacija.Ekscentrični pisac krimića Andrew Wyke poziva Miloa Tindlea, ljubavnika svoje žene u kuću kako bi ga nagovorio na pljačku koja treba da rezultira prevarom osiguravajućeg društva.Njuškalo je poput najuzbudljivije utakmice pune neočekivanih obrata u kojem se do samog kraja ne zna ko je pobjednik. </p>\r\n', '<p>Sniffer\r\n</p><p>\r\nSniffer, one of the most performed pieces by Anthony Schaffer, who has experienced several TV and film adaptation.Eccentric writer of detective stories Andrew Wyke invites Milo Tindlea, lover of his wife into the house to get him to the robbery, which should result in an insurance fraud society.Sniffer is like the most exciting matches full of unexpected turns in which to the end does not know who is the winner. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 442 572 ', '2016-11-29 20:00:00', 3, 'pozmladi@bih.net.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1317, 'TROLOVI 3D', 'Trolls 3D', 1145, 'trolovi', 'trolovien', '<p>Lutke trolova postale su hit u šezdestima, a osmislio ih je danski ribar Thomas Dam. Kultna igračka nastala u 1960-im godinama koja je bila omiljena mnogim generacijama nakon toga, sad stiže na velika platna. Dva glavna lika u filmu, optimistična Poppy i njezine suprotnost Branch morat će se suočiti s velikim izazovima koji će ih odvesti u šarenu avanturu o kakvoj su mogli samo sanjati...<br></p>', '<p>From the creators of Shrek comes the most smart, funny, irreverent animated comedy of the year, DreamWorks Trolls. This holiday season, enter a colorful, wondrous world populated by hilariously unforgettable characters and discover the story of the overly optimistic Trolls, with a constant song on their lips, and the comically pessimistic Bergens, who are only happy when they have trolls in their stomach. Featuring original music from Justin Timberlake, and soon-to-be classic mash-ups of songs from other popular artists, the film stars the voice talents of Anna Kendrick, Justin Timberlake, Russell Brand, James Corden, Kunal Nayyar, Ron Funches, Icona Pop, Gwen Stefani, and many more. DreamWorks TROLLS is a fresh, broad comedy filled with music, heart and hair-raising adventures. In November of 2016, nothing can prepare you for our new Troll world.<br></p>', '/look/events/5381_trols.jpg', '+387 33 567 230', '2016-11-12 11:15:00', 1, 'info@cinemacity.ba', 1, 0, 0),
