(1435, 'Brašno u venama', 'Flour in the veins', 3881, 'brasno1011', 'brasno1011en', '<p>Brašno u venama\n</p><p>\nBrašno u venama je predstava o porodici koju je rat rasuo po svijetu, a koja se poslije više od 20 godina susreće u jednom gradu, jednom stanu, jednoj noći. Ovo je ujedno i praizvedba teksta koji govori o emocionalnom i ideološkom jazu generacija i suočavanjem sa prošlošću kao bitnim segmentom budućeg života. Drama povratka, susreta, progovaranja, krivice, prevazilaženja, raspleta i  pomirenja. </p>\n\n', '<p>Flour in the veins \n</p><p>\nFlour in the veins is a play about a family that war scattered throughout the world, and that after more than 20 years encounter in a city, an apartment, a single night. This is also the premiere of the text which speaks about the emotional and ideological self-generation and dealing with the past as an important segment of the future life. Drama returns, meetings of negotiation, guilt, overcome, the outcome of the reconciliation.</p>\n\n', '', '+387 33 664 070', '2016-11-10 20:00:00', 3, 'teatarsartr@yahoo.com', 1, 0, 1),
(1440, 'Vojcek (projekt Vojcek)', 'Vojcek (projekt Vojcek)', 3881, 'vojcek1911', 'vojcek1911en', '<p>Vojcek (projekt Vojcek)\r\n</p><p>\r\nReportaža o stanju društva. Inscenacija svjetsko-vizionarske drame njemačkog pisca Georga Büchnera, koji je svojom tvorbom prednjačio ispred svog vremena. Iako se k Projektu Vojcek pristupilo slobodnije kad su u pitanju izvedbeno-izražajna sredstva, predstava je rađena u Büchnerovskom duhu, gdje pojedinac postepeno postaje žrtva Projekta moćni. Pitanje slobode kretanja i sopstvene odbrane ostaje otvoreno.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>Vojcek (projekt Vojcek)\r\n</p><p>\r\nReports on the state of the company. The staging of world-visionary drama German writer Georg Buchner, who with his formation forefront ahead of its time. Although the project Woyzeck accessed freely when it comes to implementation-expressive means, the show was performed in Büchnerovskom spirit, where one gradually becomes a victim of the Project of the powerful. The issue of freedom of movement and his defense remains open.</p>\r\n\r\n', '', ' +387 33 664 070', '2016-11-19 20:00:00', 3, 'teatarsartr@yahoo.com', 1, 0, 1),
