(1457, 'El Camino', 'El Camino', 389, 'el1511', 'el1511en', '<p>El Camino\n</p><p>\nBend koji Vas vodi na putovanje akustičnim zvucima i latino i gipsy ritmovima. Pjesme koje izvode su prepoznatljivi hitovi, ali u novim i posebnim aranžmanima. Bend čine muzičari sa dugogodišnjim iskustvom u raznim muzičkim žanrovima, od jazz-a i blues-a do etno i pop muzike.</p>\n', '\n<p>El Camino\n</p><p>\nThe band that takes you on a journey acoustic sounds and Latin and gypsy rhythms. The songs performed are recognizable hits, but in a new and special arrangements. The band consists of musicians with extensive experience in a variety of musical genres, from jazz and blues to folk and pop music.</p>\n', '', ' +387 33 837 168', '2016-11-15 21:30:00', 4, 'kontakt@citypub.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1459, 'Sunday Stories ', 'Sunday Stories ', 389, 'sunday1611', 'sunday1611en', '\r\n<p>Sunday Stories \r\n</p><p>\r\nSunday Stories, u želji da približe Jazz&Blues sarajevskoj publici, unose poseban dašak modernizacije na način što sklapaju vlastite aranžmane na već postojeće standarde.  </p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>Sunday Stories \r\n</p><p>\r\nSunday Stories, in order to approach the Jazz & Blues Sarajevo audience, bring a special touch of modernization in a way which concluded their own arrangements to existing standards.</p>\r\n', '', ' +387 33 837 168', '2016-11-16 21:30:00', 4, 'kontakt@citypub.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1461, 'A što oni?', 'And they?', 389, 'asto1711', 'asto1711en', '<p>A što oni?\n</p><p>\nBend A što oni? čini ekipa iskusnih muzičara, koji su poznati ne samo sarajevskoj sceni, već i šire, čak i van granica BiH. Frontman benda je Selam Tufekčić Tifa, itekako poznat po odličnom vokalu, atmosferi i komunikaciji, ali i emociji koju posjeduje.  </p>\n', '<p>And they?\n</p><p>\nBend What they? Makes a team of experienced musicians, who are known not only to the Sarajevo scene, but also beyond, even beyond the borders of Bosnia and Herzegovina. The frontman of the band''s Selam Tufekčić Tifa, very well known for excellent vocals, atmosphere and communication, but also emotion that possesses.</p>\n', '', ' +387 33 837 168', '2016-11-17 21:30:00', 4, 'kontakt@citypub.ba', 1, 0, 1),
