(1467, 'Anchy and The Moon Dogs', 'Anchy and The Moon Dogs', 389, 'anchy2411', 'anchy2411en', '<p>Anchy and The Moon Dogs\n</p><p>\nCity Pub se nalazi u samom središtu Sarajeva. Klub je izuzetno popularno okupljalište mladih koje prati svjetske muzičke trendove i uspješno ih prenosi bosanskohercegovačkoj i inostranoj publici što dokazuje kroz brojna gostovanja poznatih izvođača. </p>\n', '<p>Anchy and The Moon Dogs\n</p><p>\nCity Pub is located in the center of Sarajevo. The club is extremely popular hangout for young people, accompanied by world music trends and successfully transferred them to the Bosnian-Herzegovinian and international audience as evidenced by the numerous appearances by famous artists. </p>\n', '', ' +387 33 837 168', '2016-11-24 21:30:00', 4, 'kontakt@citypub.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1468, 'ProRocks', 'ProRocks', 389, 'prorocks2511', 'prorocks2511en', '<p>ProRocks\r\n</p><p>\r\nProRocks je nastupao u mnogim sarajevskim klubovima, kao i u regiji. U budućnosti planiraju rad na autorskim pjesmama i promociji. Bend za sebe kaže da su totalno nenormalni bend i da samo žele opstati u surovom svijetu BiH muzičke scene. Članovi benda ProRocks slobodno vrijeme posvećuju muzici uz koju su odrasli, pop-rock, a čija energija sa stejdža kreira odličnu atmosferu i dobru zabavu. </p>\r\n', '<p>ProRocks\r\n</p><p>\r\nProRocks has performed in many Sarajevo clubs, as well as in the region. Future planning work on copyright songs and promotion. The band describes herself as totally abnormal band and that they just want to survive in the harsh world of BH music scene. The band ProRocks free time devoted to music they''ve grown up, pop-rock, and the energy of a Stage creates a great atmosphere and a good time.</p>\r\n', '', ' +387 33 837 168', '2016-11-25 21:30:00', 4, 'kontakt@citypub.ba', 1, 0, 1),
