(1484, 'Poljubac žene pauka', 'Kiss of the Spider Woman', 305, 'poljubac1711', 'poljubac1711en', '<p>Poljubac žene pauka\r\n</p><p>\r\nTokom godina, ovaj teatar je stekao veliki ugled koji je prevazišao granice Bosne i Hercegovine kao teatar visokih umjetničkih standarda sa izuzetnim glumačkim ansamblom. U prosjeku oko 13.000 ljudi tokom godine pogleda naše predstave, a kapacitet dvorane Kamernog teatra je 160 mjesta. Svoje predstave igramo u svim zemljama regiona kao i u drugim državama Evrope..</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>Kiss of the Spider Woman\r\n</p><p>\r\nOver the years, the theater has gained a great reputation that has transcended the borders of Bosnia and Herzegovina as a theater of high artistic standards with exceptional acting ensemble. On average about 13,000 people during the year view of our performance, and capacity of the hall of Chamber Theatre has 160 seats. His performances playing in all countries of the region as well as in other countries of Europe..</p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 550 475', '2016-11-17 20:00:00', 3, 'info@kamerniteatar55.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1485, 'Umri muški', 'Die Hard ', 305, 'umri2211', 'umri2211en', '<p>Umri muški\r\n</p><p>\r\nPredstava Umri muški je nastala davne 1990. kao diplomska predstava Tatjane Šojić, i od tada nije prestala puniti salu Kamernog teatra 55 i doživjela je preko 250 izvođenja postavši najizvođenijom bosanskohercegovačkom predstavom svih vremena. Nastala kao nepretenciozna i niskobudžetna komedija o muško-ženskim odnosima.</p>\r\n', '<p>Die Hard \r\n</p><p>\r\nThe play Die Hard was created back in 1990 as a graduation performance Tatjana Šojić, and since then has not stopped charging hall Chamber Theatre 55 and has undergone more than 250 performance by becoming the Bosnian most performed play all the time. It was created as an unpretentious and low-budget comedy about male-female relationships.</p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 550 475', '2016-11-22 20:00:00', 3, 'info@kamerniteatar55.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1487, 'Veče italijanskih vina', 'Veče italijanskih vinaen', 66, 'veče1611', 'veče1611en', '<p>\r\n\r\nNoc italijanskih vina kompanije Only VIP d.o.o.\r\nPozivamo vas na ugodno druženje uz vrhunska italijanska vina i odličnu hranu i tamburaše u Restoranu Zembilj.\r\nVina koja služimo:\r\n1. Chianti Toscana Marzocchi DOCG - Toscana\r\n2. Nero d Avola Sicilia Marzocchi - Sicilija\r\n3. San Michele Toscana Marzocchi - Toscana\r\nPetak 18.11.2016 u 20:00h Noc italijanskih vina uz tamburaše u restoranu Zembilj.\r\n\r\n</p>', '<p>\r\n\r\nNight of Italian wine company Only VIP d.o.o\r\nWe invite you to spend pleasant evening with top quality Italian wines and great food in restaurant Zembilj.\r\nThe wines we serve:\r\nFirst Chianti DOCG Toscana Marzocchi - Toscana\r\nSecond Nero d Avola Sicilia Marzocchi - Sicily\r\n3rd San Michele Toscana Marzocchi - Toscana\r\nFriday 18/11/2016 at 20: 00h Night of Italian wine with tambourine at the restaurant Zembilj.\r\n\r\n</p>', '', ' 387 33 535 999', '2016-11-18 20:00:00', 4, 'zembilj.info@gmail.com', 1, 0, 1),
(1488, 'Muzika u živo', 'Live Music', 2403, 'live1611', 'live1611en', '<P>\r\n\r\nSvake subote od 20:30h live muzika u restoranu Ahar.\r\nU vrijeme poslovne, porodične ili intimne večere, prijaće Vam dobra zabavna, evergrin ili sevdah muzika uživo.U večernjim časovima, u prijatnom ambijentu restorana, atmosferu će Vam uljepšati tihi zvuci akustične ambijentalne muzike.\r\nZa rezervacije tel.0671171777\r\nDobro nam došli.\r\n\r\n</p>', '<p>\r\n\r\nEvery Saturday from 20: 30h live music in the restaurant Ahar.\r\nAt the time of the business, family or intimate dinner, you can listen to good fun, evergreen or sevdah music live.In eveningtime in pleasant atmosphere of the restaurant, the atmosphere will brighten soft acoustic ambient music.\r\nFor reservations tel.0671171777\r\nWelcome.\r\n\r\n</P>', '', ' 387 67 1171 777', '2016-11-19 20:30:00', 4, '', 1, 0, 1),
(1489, 'DEVET ŽIVOTA', 'Nine Lives', 1145, 'devetz', 'devetzen', '<p>Tom Brand je milijarder, radoholičar, na vrhuncu svoje karijere. Međutim, taj način života ga je udaljio od njegove prekrasne žene i kćeri Rebecce. Bliži se jedanaest rođendan njegove kćeri i ono što je oduvijek htjela bila je mačka, koju nikada nije dobila. Tom mrzi mačke, ali kako mu vrijeme za kupovinu poklona ističe, odluči se na njenu kupovinu. U toj potrazi završi u mističnom dućanu s ekscentričnim vlasnikom - Felixom Perkinsom (Christopher Walken), koji mu predstavlja veličanstvenu mačku, zvanu Mr. Fuzzypants. Na putu da donese kćeri ljubimca iz snova, dogodi se nešto bizarno te se Tom nađe zarobljen u tijelu gospodina Fuzzypants. Usvojen od svoje obitelji kao mačka Fuzzypants, Tom počinje gledati na svoj život i obitelj drugim očima...<br></p>', '<p>Tom Brand (Kevin Spacey) is a daredevil billionaire at the top of his game. His eponymous company FireBrand is nearing completion on its greatest achievement to date - the tallest skyscraper in the northern hemisphere. But Tom''s workaholic lifestyle has disconnected him from his family, particularly his beautiful wife Lara (Jennifer Garner) and his adoring daughter Rebecca (Malina Weissman). Rebecca''s 11th birthday is here, and she wants the gift she wants every year, a cat. Tom hates cats, but he is without a gift and time is running out. His GPS directs him to a mystical pet store brimming with odd and exotic cats- where the store''s eccentric owner- Felix Perkins (Christopher Walken), presents him with a majestic tomcat, named Mr. Fuzzypants. En route to present his daughter with her dream pet, a bizarre turn of events finds Tom trapped inside the body of Mr. Fuzzypants. Adopted by his own family, he begins to experience what life is truly like for the family pet, and as a cat, Tom<br></p>', '/look/events/7205_devz.jpg', '+387 33 567 230', '2016-11-19 11:40:00', 1, 'info@cinemacity.ba', 1, 0, 0),
