(1565, 'Otkrivanje žene', 'Discovering woman', 100, 'zene112', 'zene112en', '<p>Otkrivanje žene\r\n</p><p>\r\nOtkrivanje žene je dramski tekst Harisa Pašovića, suvremenog pisca i redatelja koji na neuobičajen i sistematičan način primjećuje i analizira pojave u našem društvu. Sam dramski tekst je nastajao u toku procesa postavljanja predstave. Otkrivanje žene razmatra egzistenciju žene na Balkanu kroz vijekove.</p>\r\n', '<p>Discovering woman\r\n</p><p>\r\nDiscovering Woman is a dramatic text by Haris, contemporary writer and director who in an unusual and systematically observes and analyzes phenomena in our society. Dramatic piece was created in the process of setting performances. Discovering Woman is considering existence of a woman in the Balkans over the centuries. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 226 431', '2016-12-01 19:30:00', 3, 'info@nps.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1566, 'Omer i Merima', 'Omer and Merima', 100, 'omer212', 'omer212en', '<p>Omer i Merima\r\n</p><p>\r\nVelika i nezaboravna ljubav dvoje mladih opisana u baladi Omer i Merima bila je najveća inspiracija za kreiranje ove baletne predstave. Po prvi put na našoj baletnoj sceni donosimo jednu od najpoznatijih i najljepših bosanskohercegovačkih lirskih pjesama koja zasigurno spada u sam vrh najznačajnijih djela naše narodne poezije. Priča je to o čežnji, nadi i očekivanju nikada ispunjenog sna. Balada Omer i Merima kao dragulj naše kulturne baštine sinonim je jednog vremena, ali i metafora jedne univerzalne i svevremene ljubavi. </p>\r\n', '<p>Omer and Merima\r\n</p><p>\r\nGreat and unforgettable love young couple described in the ballad of Omer and Merima was the biggest inspiration for this ballet. For the first time on our ballet scene bringing one of the most beautiful Bosnian lyrical songs that certainly belongs to the top of the most important works of our national poetry. It is a story of longing, hope and anticipation never fulfilled dream. The Ballad of Omer and Merima as a jewel of our cultural heritage is a synonym of an era, but also a metaphor for a universal and timeless love. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 226 431', '2016-12-02 19:30:00', 3, 'info@nps.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1567, 'Otkrivanje žene', 'Discovering woman', 100, 'zene23412', 'zene2312en', '<p>Otkrivanje žene\r\n</p><p>\r\nOtkrivanje žene je dramski tekst Harisa Pašovića, suvremenog pisca i redatelja koji na neuobičajen i sistematičan način primjećuje i analizira pojave u našem društvu. Sam dramski tekst je nastajao u toku procesa postavljanja predstave. Otkrivanje žene razmatra egzistenciju žene na Balkanu kroz vijekove. </p>\r\n', '<p>Discovering woman\r\n</p><p>\r\nDiscovering Woman is a dramatic text by Haris, contemporary writer and director who in an unusual and systematically observes and analyzes phenomena in our society. Dramatic piece was created in the process of setting performances. Discovering Woman is considering existence of a woman in the Balkans over the centuries. </p>', '', '+387 33 226 431', '2016-12-23 19:30:00', 3, 'info@nps.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1568, 'Tata lav i njegova sretna djeca', 'Daddy lion and his happy children', 3882, 'lav2011', 'lav2011en', '<p> Tata lav i njegova sretna djeca\r\n</p><p>\r\nTata Lav i njegova sretna djeca je jednostavan teatarski priručnik za odgoj djece: sreća je uvijek na prvom mjestu! I svi moraju biti sretni. Sretna porodica je ispunjena zvukom, svjetlom, bojama, ritmom, plesom, nesputanim pokretom i smijehom, uvijek spremna da poleti na krilima razigrane dječije mašte, pa i na mjesec ako treba. </p>\r\n', '<p>Daddy lion and his happy children\r\n</p><p>\r\nDaddy Lion and his happy children is simple theater manual for raising children: happiness is always in the first place! And everyone should be happy. Happy family is filled with sound, light, color, rhythm, dance, unrestricted movement and laughter, always ready to fly on the wings of playful children''s imagination, even a month if need be.  </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 442 572', '2016-11-20 11:00:00', 3, 'pozmladi@bih.net.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1569, 'Viana', 'Viana', 505, 'viana2011', 'viana2011en', '<p>Viana\r\n</p><p>\r\nMlada žena koristi svoje navigacijske talente kako bi otplovila do čuvenih otoka. U avanturi joj se pridružuje njen junak, polubog Maui. </p>\r\n', '<p>Viana\r\n</p><p>\r\nA young woman uses her navigational talents to set sail for a fabled island. Joining her on the adventure is her hero, the legendary demi-god Maui. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 668 186', '2016-11-20 11:00:00', 1, 'info@kinomeetingpoint.ba', 1, 0, 0),
(1570, 'Salsa Night', 'Salsa Night', 1487, 'salsa2011', 'salsa2011en', '<p> Salsa Night\r\n</p><p>\r\nUživajte u večeri uz salsu, bachata i reggeaton u Coloseum klubu.  </p>\r\n', '<p> Salsa Night\r\n</p><p>\r\nEnjoy the evening with salsa, bachata and reggeaton in Cinemas Club.  </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 250 860', '2016-11-20 20:00:00', 4, 'marketing@coloseum-club.com', 1, 0, 1),
(1571, 'Ustav Republike Hrvatske', 'The Constitution', 505, 'ustav2111', 'ustav2111en', '<p>Ustav Republike Hrvatske\r\n</p><p>\r\nPriča o četvero ljudi koji žive u istoj zgradi i zaziru jedni od drugih jer se razlikuju po imovinskom statusu, seksualnim navikama, nacionalnosti i vjeri. </p>\r\n', '<p>The Constitution\r\n</p><p>\r\nThe story follows four people who live in the same building, but avoid each other because of the differences in their assets, sexual habits, nationality and religion. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 668 186', '2016-11-21 20:00:00', 1, 'info@kinomeetingpoint.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1572, 'NEnormalni Balašević tribute band u Sarajevu', 'NEnormalni Balašević tribute band u Sarajevu', 2505, 'balasevic912', 'balasevic912en', '<p>NEnormalni Balašević tribute band u Sarajevu\r\n</p><p>\r\nClub Cinemas Sloga pruža ugodnu zabavu uz raznovrstan program: muzika uživo, klubski koncerti, tematske i salsa večeri, te muziku uz resident DJ-a.Nemojte se iznenaditi ukoliko u našem Club-u naiđete na događaje koje još uvijek niste imali priliku vidjeti u našem gradu.\r\nTrudimo se da svaki vaš izlazak bude ugodan i zabavan. </p>\r\n', '<p>NEnormalni Balašević tribute band u Sarajevu\r\n</p><p>\r\nClub Cinemas Sloga provides pleasant entertainment with a varied program: live music, club concerts, thematic and salsa nights, and music with resident DJ.Do not be surprised if in our Club you encounter events that have not yet experienced in our city.\r\nWe try to make your every night out enjoyable and fun. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 218 811', '2016-12-09 20:00:00', 4, 'info@cinemas.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1573, 'Zoster', 'Zoster', 2505, 'zoster2312', 'zoster2312en', '<p>Zoster\r\n</p><p>\r\nClub Cinemas Sloga pruža ugodnu zabavu uz raznovrstan program: muzika uživo, klubski koncerti, tematske i salsa večeri, te muziku uz resident DJ-a.Nemojte se iznenaditi ukoliko u našem Club-u naiđete na događaje koje još uvijek niste imali priliku vidjeti u našem gradu.\r\nTrudimo se da svaki vaš izlazak bude ugodan i zabavan. </p>\r\n', '<p>Zoster\r\n</p><p>\r\nClub Cinemas Sloga provides pleasant entertainment with a varied program: live music, club concerts, thematic and salsa nights, and music with resident DJ.Do not be surprised if in our Club you encounter events that have not yet experienced in our city.\r\nWe try to make your every night out enjoyable and fun. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 218 811', '2016-12-23 21:00:10', 4, 'info@cinemas.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1574, 'Cafe Society', 'Cafe Society', 505, 'cafe2211', 'cafe2211en', '<p>Cafe Society\r\n</p><p>\r\nGodine 1930. mladić rođen u Bronxu seli u Hollywood gdje se zaljubljuje u sekretaricu svog moćnog strica, agenta za glumce. Po povratku u New York on upada u svijet noćnog života visokog društva. </p>\r\n', '<p>Cafe Society\r\n</p><p>\r\nIn the 1930s, a young Bronx native moves to Hollywood, where he falls in love with the secretary of his powerful uncle, an agent to the stars. After returning to New York, he is swept up in the vibrant world of high society nightclub life. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 668 186', '2016-11-22 20:00:00', 1, 'info@kinomeetingpoint.ba', 1, 0, 0),
(1575, 'Umri muški', 'Die Hard', 305, 'umri2311', 'umri2311en', '<p>Umri muški\r\n</p><p>\r\nPredstava Umri muški je nastala davne 1990. kao diplomska predstava Tatjane Šojić, i od tada nije prestala puniti salu Kamernog teatra 55 i doživjela je preko 250 izvođenja postavši najizvođenijom bosanskohercegovačkom predstavom svih vremena. Nastala kao nepretenciozna i niskobudžetna komedija o muško-ženskim odnosima, Umri muški je, isključivo zahvaljujući neprekidnom interesu publike, postala kultna predstava Kamernog teatra 55. Eva, Bruno i Mario u briljantnoj interpretaciji Tatajane Šojić, Admira Glamočaka i Senada Bašića postali su tako junaci čije replike njihovi brojni fanovi, koji su predstavu gledali i po deset, petnaest ili dvadeset puta, znaju napamet, uvijek u njima otkrivajući novu istinitost, životnost i duhovitost. </p>\r\n', '<p>Die Hard\r\n</p><p>\r\nThe play Die Hard was created back in 1990 as a graduation performance Tatjana Šojić, and since then has not stopped charging hall Chamber Theatre 55 and has undergone more than 250 performing becoming the most performed & H performance of all time. It was created as an unpretentious and low-budget comedy about male-female relationships, Die Hard is exclusively due to the continuous interest of the public, has become a cult performances Chamber Theatre 55. Eva, Bruno and Mario in a brilliant interpretation Tatajana Šojić, Admira Glamočak and Senad Basic become so heroes whose replicas of their numerous fans, who have watched the show for ten, fifteen or twenty times, they know by heart, always in them revealing new veracity, vitality and wit. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 550 475', '2016-11-23 20:00:00', 3, 'info@kamerniteatar55.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1576, '15. Ciklus španske kinematografije: Najmanje ostrvo', '15. Ciklus španske kinematografije: Najmanje ostrvo', 505, 'ostrvo2411', 'ostrvo2411en', '<p>15. Ciklus španske kinematografije: Najmanje ostrvo\r\n</p><p>\r\nŠpanija, početkom 80-tih godina prošlog vijeka. Dvojica policajaca, uzajamno suprostavljenih ličnih ideologija, po zadatku iz Madrida odlaze u izolovano seoce na jugu, smješteno u močvari Guadalquivira, kako bi istražili nestanak dvije mlade djevojke.Boraveći u ovoj zajednici zaglavljenoj u prošlosti, policajci ne samo da će morati da se souče sa okrutnim ubicom, već i sa sopstvenim avetima. </p>\r\n', '<p>15. Ciklus španske kinematografije: Najmanje ostrvo\r\n</p><p>\r\nSpain, early 1980s. Two police officers with deep divisions in their personal ideology are dispatched from Madrid to a remote village in the Guadalquivir Marshes in the south of the country to investigate the disappearance of two young women. While living in the community that is stuck in the past, the police officers will not only have to confront a cruel killer, but also the ghosts of their past. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 668 186', '2016-11-24 20:00:00', 1, 'info@kinomeetingpoint.ba', 1, 0, 0),
(1577, 'U Zvorniku ja sam ostavio svoje srce', 'In Zvornik I Have Left My Heart', 305, 'zvornik2411', 'zvornik2411en', '<p>U Zvorniku ja sam ostavio svoje srce\r\n</p><p>\r\nTekst jednog od najpoznatijih bh. pisaca Abdulaha Sidrana U Zvorniku ja sam ostavio svoje srce nesumnjivo spada u sam vrh domaćeg dramskog stvaralaštva. To je tekst koji koji govori o samom početku rata u BiH, o mučnoj golgoti koju su ljudi iz istočne Bosne prolazili samo radi razlike u imenu i prezimenu. O nadi i beznađu. Radnja drame odvija se u Zvorniku, pred sami početak rata. Rudo, nastavnik muzike i horovođa, je amater dirigent koji sanja da jednog dana napiše simfoniju o rijeci Drini, inspirisan Smetaninom Vltavom. Prilikom povratka s jednog takmičenja školskih horova, Rudo svoje učenike šalje natrag u Sarajevo, a on svraća u svoj rodni Zvornik. </p>\r\n', '<p>In Zvornik I Have Left My Heart\r\n</p><p>\r\nThe text of one of the most popular BH. writers Abdulah Sidran In Zvornik I Have Left My Heart undoubtedly one of the top domestic dramatic art. This is a text that speaks of the beginning of the Bosnian war, have seen the Golgotha that people from eastern Bosnia passed only for the difference in the first and last name. About the hope and hopelessness. The play takes place in Zvornik, just before the war. Rudo, a music teacher and choirmaster, is an amateur conductor who dreams of one day write a symphony about the Drina River, inspired Smetana Vltava. Upon returning from one competition of school choirs, Rudo his disciples sent back to Sarajevo, and he draws in his native Zvornik. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 550 475', '2016-11-24 20:00:00', 3, 'info@kamerniteatar55.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1578, 'Lako je živjeti zatvorenih očiju', 'Living is easy with eyes closed', 505, 'zivjeti2511', 'zivjeti2511en', '<p>Lako je živjeti zatvorenih očiju\r\n</p><p>\r\nAntonio (Javier Cámara) je nastavnik engleskog u Španiji 1966. godine, koji na svojim časovima koristi pjesme Beatlesa kao nastavno sredstvo. Kad sazna da je njegov idol John Lennon došao u Almeriju na snimanje filma, odluči da ga potraži i upozna. Usput poveze Juanja (Francesc Colomer), 16-godišnjaka koji je pobjegao od kuće i Belén (Natalia de Molina), 21-godišnjakinju koja također izgleda kao da bježi od nečega. </p>\r\n', '<p>Living is easy with eyes closed\r\n</p><p>\r\nAntonio (Javier Cámara) works as an English language teacher in Spain in 1966 and uses Beatles songs as a learning tool. On hearing that John Lennon is filming in Almeria, Antonio decides to drive there in hope of meeting him. Along the way, Antonio picks up 16-year-old Juanja (Francesc Colomer) who has run away from home and 21-year-old Belén (Natalia de Molina) who also appears to be running away from something. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 668 186', '2016-11-25 20:00:00', 1, 'info@kinomeetingpoint.ba', 1, 0, 0),
(1579, 'Svi su mrtvi', 'They are all dead', 505, 'svi2611', 'svi2611en', '<p>Svi su mrtvi\r\n</p><p>\r\nLupe (Elena Anaya) pati od teškog oblika agorafobije, zbog čega ne izlazi iz kuće. Da je neko vidi u kućnom ogrtaču i papučama, potpuno ovisnu o mami i sa adolescentnim sinom koji je prezire, niko ne bi rekao da je u 80-tim bila rok zvijezda. Kad njenoj majci dosadi da gleda kako joj se kćer pretvara u konfliktnog egoistu, na Noć vještica odluči da popriča sa njenim sinom Diegom. Kad se ovaj vrati kući, izgleda kao i uvijek, mlad momak odsutnog pogleda; ono što situaciju čini neobičnom je to da je Diego mrtav... </p>\r\n', '<p>They are all dead\r\n</p><p>\r\nLupe (Elena Anaya) suffers from severe agoraphobia and thus never leaves her home. Anyone who sees Lupe in her house robe and slippers - completely dependent on her mother and with an adolescent son who despises her - would find it impossible to imagine that in 1980s she was a rock star. On the Day of the Dead, Lupe''s mother realizes she has had enough of watching her daughter turn into a conflict-prone egoist, so she decides to talk to her son Diego. After Diego returns home he appears to be the same young man with wondering eyes he had always been; but what makes the situation unusual is the fact that Diego is supposed to be dead... </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 668 186', '2016-11-26 20:00:00', 1, 'info@kinomeetingpoint.ba', 1, 0, 0),
(1580, 'Glavna ulica', 'Main street', 505, 'ulica2711', 'ulica2711en', '<p>Glavna ulica\r\n</p><p>\r\nStanovnici malog provincijskog grada su zarobljenici svoje arhaične tradicije i običaja.U ovom opresivnom okruženju, Isabel, neudata 35-godišnja žena, osjeća da nije uspjela u životu jer se nije udala. Juan i njegovi prijatelji, koji ubijaju dosadu smišljajući naporne šale na tuđi račun, uvjere Isabel da je Juan zaljubljen u nju i da će je zaprositi. </p>\r\n', '<p>Main street\r\n</p><p>\r\nResidents of a small, provincial Spanish town are prisoners of their archaic tradition and customs. In the town''s oppressive surrounding, 35-year-old spinster Isabel feels she had failed in life for having not married. Juan and his friends, who mitigate the boredom by plotting distasteful pranks against fellow citizens, convince Isabel that Juan is in love with her and intends to ask for her hand in marriage. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 668 186', '2016-11-27 20:00:00', 1, 'info@kinomeetingpoint.ba', 1, 0, 0),
(1581, 'Live Music', 'Live Music', 2471, 'live2511', 'live2511en', '<p>Live Music\r\n</p><p>\r\nJazz & Night Club, zvanični partner Jazz Fest Sarajevo, za više od 10 godina. Uz dugu listu bendova i umjetnika koji rade na našem Late Nite Stage kroz koncerte solo ili jam sessionima, možemo s ponosom predstaviti naš klub kao hot spot za najbolje jazz koncerte u gradu u posljednjih nekoliko godina. Naš vrt, je jedan od najboljih u srcu Sarajeva, s pogledom na Katedrale, je nešto što morate vdjeti.  </p>\r\n', '<p>Live Music\r\n</p><p>\r\nJazz & Night Club, official partner of Jazz Fest Sarajevo, for more than 10 years. With the long list of bends and artists who perform on our Late Nite Stage through the solo concerts or jam sessions, we could proudly present our club as a hot spot for best jazz concerts in city for last couple of years. Our garden, as one of finest in the heart of Sarajevo, with the view on the city cathedral, is a must see&feel place in our town.  </p>\r\n', '', '+387 61 588 884', '2016-11-25 22:30:00', 4, 'clubmonument@gmail.com', 1, 0, 1),
(1582, 'Planovi za sutra', 'Plans for tomorrow', 505, 'planovi2811', 'planovi2811en', '<p>Planovi za sutra\r\n</p><p>\r\nU toku jednog dana, Inés, Antonia, Marian i Mónica, žene različitih godišta i u veoma različitim životnim situacijama, moraju donijeti važne odluke koje bi njihove živote mogle da promijene zauvijek: Hoće li Inés zadržati trudnoću, uprkos svima i svemu? Hoće li Marian shvatiti da je njena veza s mužem završila i postupiti u skladu s tim? Šta će učiniti Antonia kada joj prava ljubav njenog života zatraži još jednu šansu, a ona je sretno udata i ima djecu? Šta će učiniti Mónica sa svojim osjećajem nemoći i željom za osvetom kad se njena porodica raspadne? </p>\r\n', '<p>Plans for tomorrow\r\n</p><p>\r\nIn a single day, four women of different ages and with different lives must make important decisions that can forever change their world. Will Inés keep her pregnancy despite everything and everyone? Will Marian realize that her relationship with her husband is truly over and act accordingly? What will Antonia do when her first love asks her for another chance despite her being happily married and with children? How will Mónica deal with her sense of hopelessness and desire for revenge after her family brakes apart? </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 668 186', '2016-11-28 20:00:00', 1, 'info@kinomeetingpoint.ba', 1, 0, 0),
(1583, 'Helem Nejse', 'Helem Nejse', 305, 'helem2811', 'helem2811en', '<p>Helem Nejse\r\n</p><p>\r\nKamerni teatar 55 osnovao je 1955. godine u Sarajevu veliki pozorišni reditelj, producent i teoretičar, Jurislav Korenić, u traganju za novim teatarskim izrazom, te iz potrebe za drugačijim teatarskim profilom od onoga koji je preovladavao u većini pozorišta tadašnje Jugoslavije. Taj novi, inovativan i tragalački pristup u teatarskoj produkciji predstavljao je stremljenje prema evropskoj avangardi toga vremena. Tokom godina, ovaj teatar je stekao veliki ugled koji je prevazišao granice Bosne i Hercegovine kao teatar visokih umjetničkih standarda sa izuzetnim glumačkim ansamblom. U prosjeku oko 13.000 ljudi tokom godine pogleda naše predstave, a kapacitet dvorane Kamernog teatra je 160 mjesta. Svoje predstave igramo u svim zemljama regiona kao i u drugim državama Evrope. </p>\r\n', '<p>Helem Nejse\r\n</p><p>\r\nChamber Theatre 55 was founded in 1955 in Sarajevo great theater director, producer and theorist, Jurislav Korenić, in search of new theatrical expression, and of the need for a different theater profile than that prevailing in most theaters of the former Yugoslavia. This new, innovative and an inquiring approach to theater production was the tendency of the European avant-garde of the time. Over the years, the theater has gained a great reputation that has transcended the borders of Bosnia and Herzegovina as a theater of high artistic standards with exceptional acting ensemble. On average about 13,000 people during the year view of our performance, and capacity of the hall of Chamber Theatre has 160 seats. His performances playing in all countries of the region as well as in other countries of Europe. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 550 475', '2016-11-28 20:00:00', 3, 'info@kamerniteatar55.ba', 1, 0, 1),
