(1586, 'Majstor i Margarita', 'The Master and Margarita', 3881, 'majstor2911', 'majstor2911en', '<p>Majstor i Margarita\r\n</p><p>\r\nSarajevski ratni teatar SARTR utemeljen je 17. maja 1992. godine na inicijativu reditelja Dubravka Bibanovića i Gradimira Gojera, ing. Đorđa Mačkića i pisca Safeta Plakala, a okupio je glumce i ine saradnike iz tri profesionalna sarajevska teatra koja su, zbog agresije na Bosnu i Hercegovinu, morala obustaviti svoj rad. </p>\r\n', '<p>The Master and Margarita\r\n</p><p>\r\nSarajevo War Theater SARTR was established on 17 May 1992 at the initiative of directors Dubravko Bibanović and side, especially baring ing. George Mackic and writer Safet cried, and brought together actors and various associates from three professional Sarajevo theaters which, because of the aggression on Bosnia and Herzegovina, had to suspend its work. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 664 070', '2016-11-29 20:00:00', 3, 'sartr.info@gmail.com', 1, 0, 1),
