(1597, 'DR. MOTTE & JEAN MARIE K', 'DR. MOTTE & JEAN MARIE K', 2505, 'dr0212', 'dr0212en', '<p>DR. MOTTE & JEAN MARIE K\r\n</p><p>\r\nClub Cinemas Sloga pruža ugodnu zabavu uz raznovrstan program: muzika uživo, klubski koncerti, tematske i salsa večeri, te muziku uz resident DJ-a.Nemojte se iznenaditi ukoliko u našem Club-u naiđete na događaje koje još uvijek niste imali priliku vidjeti u našem gradu.\r\nTrudimo se da svaki vaš izlazak bude ugodan i zabavan. </p>\r\n', '<p>DR. MOTTE & JEAN MARIE K\r\n</p><p>\r\nClub Cinemas Sloga provides pleasant entertainment with a varied program: live music, club concerts, thematic and salsa nights, and music with resident DJ.Do not be surprised if in our Club you encounter events that have not yet experienced in our city.\r\nWe try to make your every night out enjoyable and fun. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 218 811', '2016-12-02 21:00:00', 4, 'info@cinemas.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1600, 'Sunce tuđeg neba', 'Sun of foreign skies', 5668, 'sunce0112 ', 'sunce0112 en', '<p>Sunce tuđeg neba\r\n</p><p>\r\nJunak ove priče je višenacionalan i multikulturalan i kao takav se našao u situaciji da luta svijetom tražeći svoje nebo, svoj novi spas. U pokušaju da se prilagodi novoj sredini, junak ove predstave prolazi kroz mnoštvo situacija i stanja koje idu od euforičnog oduševljenja do neuroze, bijesa. Konstantno upoređuje svoj novi dom s onim koji je ostavio iza sebe, donoseći zaključke koje će biti obojene zdravim humorom. </p>\r\n', '<p>Sun of foreign skies\r\n</p><p>\r\n The hero of this story is a multi-ethnic and multicultural and as such found himself wandering the world asking your sky, your new salvation. In an attempt to adapt to the new environment, the hero of the play goes through a multitude of situations and conditions that go from euphoric enthusiasm to neurosis, anger. We constantly compare their new home with those who were left behind, drawing conclusions that will be painted a healthy humor.</p>\r\n\r\n', '', '+387 33 201 203', '2016-12-01 20:00:00', 3, 'info@skenderija.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1601, '6 Novogodišnji ZUMBA PARTY', '6 New Year ZUMBA PARTY', 5668, '6novogodisnji0312 ', '6novogodisnji0312en', '<p>6 Novogodišnji ZUMBA PARTY\r\n</p><p>\r\n6 Novogodišnji Zumba party/MASTERCLASS :\r\nI ove godine vas očekuje najbolja plesna dvorana u regionu,perfektno ozvučenje i rasvjeta,dobri domačini , grad Sarajevo i jedinstvena ZUMBA familija.</p>\r\n', '<p>6 New Year ZUMBA PARTY\r\n</p><p>\r\n6 New Year Zumba party / MASTERCLASS:\r\nThis year you can expect the best ballroom in the region, perfect sound system and lighting, good locals, the city of Sarajevo and unique ZUMBA family. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 201 203', '2016-12-03 18:00:00', 4, 'info@skenderija.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1603, 'Koncert  PETAR GRAŠO', 'Concert PETAR GRAŠO', 5668, 'koncert 2511', 'koncert 2511en', '<p>Koncert  PETAR GRAŠO\r\n</p><p>\r\nU Domu mladih su se pored koncertnih dešavanja održavala tradicionalna vjenčanja, brucoške večeri, proglašenja diplomanata, Crveni karanfil, i slično. U ovom omladinskom centru djelovao je i Književni klub, zatim brojne redakcije za filmske, scenske, kulturne, muzičke, likovne i izdavačke programe, a kroz sve ovo nudila se mogućnost mladima da se okušaju i kao autori. </p>\r\n', '<p>Koncert  PETAR GRAŠO\r\n</p><p>\r\nIn the Youth House the next concert events held a traditional wedding, the freshman dinner, declaration of graduates, Red Carnation, and the like. This youth center is operated and Literary Club, numerous editorial boards for film, theater, culture, music, art and publishing programs, and through this provide the opportunity for young people to try and as authors.</p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 201 203', '2016-11-25 20:00:00', 4, 'info@skenderija.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1604, 'Diplomatic Winter Bazar', 'Diplomatic Winter Bazar', 5668, 'diplomatic0312', 'diplomatic0312', '<p>Diplomatic Winter Bazar\r\n</p><p>\r\nGodišnji zima Bazaar je postao tradicija u Sarajevu omogućava ambasadama, nevladinim organizacijama i proizvođače da dođu zajedno da ponudi veliki izbor primamljive hrane, pića, rukotvorine i još mnogo toga. Bazar će također sadrže raznoliku zabave za odrasle i djecu tokom dana da garantuje da će ovo biti zabavno događaj, ne treba propustiti.\r\nSredstva prikupljena će ići u pravcu tri dostojan uzroka fokusirajući se na širok spektar društvenih i obrazovnih pitanja u cijeloj Bosni i Hercegovini.</p>\r\n', '<p>Diplomatic Winter Bazar\r\n</p><p>\r\nThe annual winter bazaar has become a tradition in Sarajevo allowing Embassies, NGOs and vendors to come together to offer a wide selection of tantalizing food, drinks, handicrafts and much more. The bazaar will also feature a variety of entertainment for adults and children throughout the day to guarantee that this will be a fun-filled event, not to be missed. \r\nFunds raised will go towards three worthy causes focusing on a wide range of social and educational issues across Bosnia and Herzegovina.</p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 201 203', '2016-12-03 11:00:00', 5, 'info@skenderija.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1606, 'Balet na ledu', 'Ballet on Ice', 5668, 'balet1212 ', 'balet1212en', '<p>Balet na ledu\r\n</p><p>\r\nSt. Petersburg državni balet jedan je od bisera Rusije osnovan 1967. godine. Ova baletna skupina nudi pravi klasični balet s klasičnim baletnim kostimima, a koji se izvodi na specijalnom klizalištu.\r\nAnsambl sastoji se od plesača/klizača, a većina njih bili su vrhunski klizači u pojedinačnom te klizanju u parovima gdje su osvojili i brojne medalje.Članovi baleta kombinacijom umjetničkog klizanja i klasičnog ruskog baleta osvajaju publiku diljem svijeta na najprestižnijim pozornicama, a do sada su imali više od 7 hiljada nastupa na rasprodanim najprestižnijim pozornicama.\r\n</p>\r\n', '<p>Ballet on Ice\r\n</p><p>\r\nSt. Petersburg State Ballet is one of the jewels of Russia was established in 1967. This ballet group offers real classical ballet with classical ballet costume, which is carried on a special rink.\r\nThe ensemble consists of dancers / slider, and most of them were top skaters in singles and in pairs skating where they won numerous medalje.Members ballet combination of figure skating and classical Russian ballet conquered audiences around the world at the most prestigious stages, and so far they had more than 7,000 sold-out performances at the most prestigious stages.\r\n</p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 201 203', '2016-12-12 20:00:00', 5, 'info@skenderija.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1608, 'Techno Love', 'Techno Love', 5668, 'techno1712', 'techno1712en', '<p>Techno Love\r\n</p><p>\r\nZa dobar provod zaduženi su fenomenalna Lea Dobričić (Srbija), majstor techno vibracija David Temessi (Mađarska) i sjajni artisti sa domaće scene Worda, Vontech, Drzneday i Rajvosound Crew.\r\n</p>\r\n', '<p>Techno Love\r\n</p><p>\r\nFor a good time charge phenomenal Lea Dobričić (Serbia), a master of techno vibration David Temessi (Hungary) and brilliant artists from the local scene Word, Vontech, Drzneday and Rajvosound Crew.</p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 201 203', '2016-12-17 22:00:00', 4, 'info@skenderija.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1609, 'Maša i Medvjed', 'Masha and the Bear', 5668, 'masa2212', 'masa2212en', '<p>Maša i Medvjed\r\n</p><p>\r\nDolazi nam sjajna pozorišna predstava za djecu, nastala po istoimenom, trenutno najpopularnijem, animiranom filmu Maša i Medvjed koja osvaja velike i male.\r\nOva predstava u izvođenju glumaca dječijeg Moskovskog teatra sihronizovana je na bosanski jezik, i napravljena je po motivima najpopularnijeg animiranog filma, zvanično proglašenog za najbolji i najedukativniji crtani film u Evropi u posljednjih 20 godina.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>Masha and the Bear\r\n</p><p>\r\nWe''ve got a great theater play for children, created by the same name, is currently the most popular, animated movie Masha and the Bear, which won the large and small.\r\nThe play performed by actors of the Moscow children''s theater is synchronized to the Bosnian language, and made by motifs of the most popular animated film, officially declared the best ways you can visit a cartoon in Europe in the last 20 years.</p>\r\n', '', ' 387 33 201 203', '2016-12-22 18:00:00', 5, 'info@skenderija.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1610, 'Badminton turnir SaOpen', 'Badminton turnir SaOpen', 5668, 'turnir2611', 'turnir2611en', '<p>Badminton turnir SaOpen\r\n</p><p>\r\nRekreacija za sve generacije i omiljeni porodični sport. Badminton sekcija Udruženja - klub sporta i rekreacije za sve je lokacija za druženje, zabavu i smijeh. Pridružite nam se. </p>\r\n', '<p>Badminton turnir SaOpen\r\n</p><p>\r\nRecreation for all ages and favorite family sport. Badminton Association section - club sports and recreation for all the locations for socializing, fun and laughter. Join us. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 201 203', '2016-11-26 08:30:00', 5, 'info@skenderija.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1611, 'Salsa Night', 'Salsa Night', 1487, 'salsa2711', 'salsa2711en', '<p> Salsa Night\r\n</p><p>\r\nUživajte u večeri uz salsu, bachata i reggeaton u Coloseum klubu.  </p>\r\n', '<p> Salsa Night\r\n</p><p>\r\nEnjoy the evening with salsa, bachata and reggeaton in Cinemas Club.  </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 250 860', '2016-11-27 20:00:00', 4, 'marketing@coloseum-club.com', 1, 0, 1),
(1612, 'TROLOVI 3D', 'Trolls 3D', 1145, 'trolovi', 'trolovien', '<p>Lutke trolova postale su hit u šezdestima, a osmislio ih je danski ribar Thomas Dam. Kultna igračka nastala u 1960-im godinama koja je bila omiljena mnogim generacijama nakon toga, sad stiže na velika platna. Dva glavna lika u filmu, optimistična Poppy i njezine suprotnost Branch morat će se suočiti s velikim izazovima koji će ih odvesti u šarenu avanturu o kakvoj su mogli samo sanjati...<br></p>', '<p>From the creators of Shrek comes the most smart, funny, irreverent animated comedy of the year, DreamWorks Trolls. This holiday season, enter a colorful, wondrous world populated by hilariously unforgettable characters and discover the story of the overly optimistic Trolls, with a constant song on their lips, and the comically pessimistic Bergens, who are only happy when they have trolls in their stomach. Featuring original music from Justin Timberlake, and soon-to-be classic mash-ups of songs from other popular artists, the film stars the voice talents of Anna Kendrick, Justin Timberlake, Russell Brand, James Corden, Kunal Nayyar, Ron Funches, Icona Pop, Gwen Stefani, and many more. DreamWorks TROLLS is a fresh, broad comedy filled with music, heart and hair-raising adventures. In November of 2016, nothing can prepare you for our new Troll world.<br></p>', '/look/events/5381_trols.jpg', '+387 33 567 230', '2016-11-26 11:20:00', 1, 'info@cinemacity.ba', 1, 0, 0),
