(1699, 'Balkanski špijun', 'Balkan spy', 100, 'balkanski0612 ', 'balkanski0612en', '<p>Balkanski špijun\r\n</p><p>\r\nNarodno pozorište Sarajevo najstariji je bosanskohercegovački profesionalni teatar. Osnovan je 1921. godine.\r\nU počecima svog djelovanja Narodno pozorište Sarajevo je djelovalo, isključivo, kao dramski teatar.\r\nOd 1946. Narodno pozorište dobiva i muzičke segmente djelovanja pa će tako bogatoj povijesti našeg teatra izuzetno donijeti Opera, odnosno Balet.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>Balkan spy\r\n</p><p>\r\nSarajevo National Theatre is the oldest professional theater in BiH. It was founded in 1921.\r\nIn the beginning of its activity Sarajevo National Theatre is operated solely as a drama theater.\r\nSince 1946, the National Theatre and gets musical segments of action and so will the rich history of our theater extremely make Opera or Ballet..</p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 226 431', '2016-12-06 19:30:00', 3, 'info@nps.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1700, 'Tamburaši - Orkestar Artis', 'Tamburaši - Orkestar Artis', 1632, 'tamburasi0112', 'tamburasi0112en', '<p>Tamburaši - Orkestar Artis\r\n</p><p>\r\nHistorija, tradicija i kvalitet na jednom mjestu, najbolje opisuju jedinstveni ugostiteljski objekat u Sarajevu – Pivnicu HS. Nalazi se u Centru Sarajeva, u dijelu Starog Grada na Bistriku, samo nekoliko metara od Sarajevske pivare, u zgradi koja je zaštićeni historijski objekt. Pored Pivnice HS nalazi se jedini muzej pivarstva u BiH. </p>\r\n', '<p>Tamburaši - Orkestar Artis\r\n</p><p>\r\nHistory, tradition and quality in one place, best describe the unique restaurant in Sarajevo - Pub HS. It is located in the center of Sarajevo, in part of the Old City in Bistrik, just a few meters from Sarajevo Brewery, in a building that is a protected historic building. In addition to the pub HS is the only brewery museum in BiH. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 239 740', '2016-12-01 21:00:00', 4, 'pivnica.hs@pivara.ba', 1, 0, 1),
