ring his more than 90 years long-acting Sarajevo National Theatre played a huge number of theater, ballet and opera performances throughout Bosnia and Herzegovina, but also abroad. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 226 431', '2016-12-06 19:30:00', 3, 'info@nps.ba', 1, 0, 1),
