(1864, 'Umri muški', 'Die Hard', 305, 'umri1312', 'umri1312en', '<p>Umri muški\r\n</p><p>\r\nPredstava Umri muški je nastala davne 1990. kao diplomska predstava Tatjane Šojić, i od tada nije prestala puniti salu Kamernog teatra 55 i doživjela je preko 250 izvođenja postavši najizvođenijom bosanskohercegovačkom predstavom svih vremena. Nastala kao nepretenciozna i niskobudžetna komedija o muško-ženskim odnosima, Umri muški je, isključivo zahvaljujući neprekidnom interesu publike, postala kultna predstava Kamernog teatra 55. Eva, Bruno i Mario u briljantnoj interpretaciji Tatajane Šojić, Admira Glamočaka i Senada Bašića postali su tako junaci čije replike njihovi brojni fanovi, koji su predstavu gledali i po deset, petnaest ili dvadeset puta, znaju napamet, uvijek u njima otkrivajući novu istinitost, životnost i duhovitost. </p>\r\n', '<p>Die Hard\r\n</p><p>\r\nThe play Die Hard was created back in 1990 as a graduation performance Tatjana Šojić, and since then has not stopped charging hall Chamber Theatre 55 and has undergone more than 250 performing becoming the most performed & H performance of all time. It was created as an unpretentious and low-budget comedy about male-female relationships, Die Hard is exclusively due to the continuous interest of the public, has become a cult performances Chamber Theatre 55. Eva, Bruno and Mario in a brilliant interpretation Tatajana Šojić, Admira Glamočak and Senad Basic become so heroes whose replicas of their numerous fans, who have watched the show for ten, fifteen or twenty times, they know by heart, always in them revealing new veracity, vitality and wit. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 550 475', '2016-12-13 20:00:00', 3, 'info@kamerniteatar55.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(1865, 'Scream for me Sarajevo', 'Scream for me Sarajevo', 505, 'scream1312', 'scream1312en', '<p>Scream for me Sarajevo\r\n</p><p>\r\nDokumentarni film o Sarajevu pod opsadom, muzici u gradu, s akcentom na 14. decembar 1994. i koncert Brucea Dickinsona u BKC-u. O ljudima koji su rizikovali svoje živote da bi svirali pred ljudima koji su rizikovali svoje živote da bi živjeli. </p>\r\n', '<p>Scream for me Sarajevo\r\n</p><p>\r\nA documentary film about Sarajevo during the 1992-95 siege; specifically a film about the music scene in the besieged Bosnian capital with special focus on a concert held in the city’s BKC music hall by Bruce Dickinson on December 14, 1994. It is a film about people who risked their lives to perform for the people who risked their lives in order to live them. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 668 186', '2016-12-13 19:00:00', 1, 'info@kinomeetingpoint.ba', 1, 0, 0),
(1866, 'Family sunday', 'Family sunday', 1644, 'family1812', 'family1812en', '<p>Family sunday\r\n</p><p>\r\nKoncept AQUARIUS SARAJEVO pokrenut je davne 1999. na Grbavici tik uz stadion (zgrada LORIS) u želji prezentiranja stečenog ugostiteljskog znanja te iskustva kako u predratnom Sarajevu tako i u inostranstvu. Nakon prvih 6 godina rada,2005. AQUARIUS seli u naselje Šoping u veći i ekskluzivniji prostor u kojem se i sada nalazi. U vječitoj želji za razvojem i profesonalnim usavršavanjem 2007. nastaje firma ZARMED d.o.o. koja se svojim kvalitetom i konstantnim poslovnim napredovanjem, Sarajlijama i gostima Grada, uspijeva nametnuti kao respektabilna firma za ugostiteljstvo i usluge. </p>\r\n', '<p>Family sunday\r\n</p><p>\r\nThe concept of Aquarius SARAJEVO was launched back in 1999 in Grbavica next to the stadium (building LORIS) in an effort to present the acquired knowledge and experience of catering to the pre-war Sarajevo and abroad. After the first 6 years of operation, the 2005th Aquarius moves to the village shopping in larger and more exclusive area in which it is situated now. In the eternal desire to develop and 2007. This professional training company formed armed Ltd. that their quality and constant business advancement, the people of Sarajevo and guests of the city, manages to impose such a respectable company for catering and services.</p>\r\n', '', '+387 61 210 788', '2016-12-18 10:00:00', 5, 'aquariussarajevo@gmail.com', 1, 0, 1),
(1867, 'Šapni ako zaboravim', 'Whisper If I Forget', 505, 'sapni0912', 'sapni0912en', '<p>Šapni ako zaboravim\n</p><p>\nHanifa je tek završila srednju medicinsku školu i počela raditi u varoškoj ambulanti. Zajedno sa svojom buntovnom sestrom Hatidžom živi u jednom malom, mirnom i konzervativnom mjestu. Koliko god je Hanifa stidljiva i povučena, toliko je Hatidža nestašna, neposlušna i svojeglava. Dok s jedne strane Hanifa, ljubitelj književnosti, čuva svesku sa  poezijom koju nikome ne pokazuje, s druge strane Hatidža toliko voli da pjeva da zaboravi sve oko sebe. Jednog dana u centar varoši dolazi Tarik, sin novog sreskog načelnika i od tog dana život ove dvije sestre u potpunosti se mijenja... </p>\n', '<p>Whisper If I Forget\n</p><p>\nHanifa has just finished Medical High School and started working as a nurse in the medical centre of the town. She lives together with her unruly sister Hatice in a small, quiet and conservative town. While Hanifa is shy and withdrawn, Hatice on the opposite is mischievous, disobedient and obstinate. While on one side Hanife is a literature lover, has a poetry note book which she doesn''t show to anyone, Hatice on the other side loves singing to the extent that she forgets about everybody. One day the newly appointed district governor''s son Tarık comes to the town center and the life of the two sisters changes completly from that day on... </p>\n', '', '+387 33 668 186', '2016-12-09 20:00:00', 1, 'info@kinomeetingpoint.ba', 1, 0, 0),
(1870, 'Hladnoća Kalandara', 'Cold of Kalandar', 505, 'hladnoca1012', 'hladnoca1012en', '<p>Hladnoća Kalandara\r\n</p><p>\r\nPriča o četvero ljudi koji žive u istoj zgradi i zaziru jedni od drugih jer se razlikuju po imovinskom statusu, seksualnim navikama, nacionalnosti i vjeri. </p>\r\n', '<p>Cold of Kalandar\r\n</p><p>\r\nThe story follows four people who live in the same building, but avoid each other because of the differences in their assets, sexual habits, nationality and religion. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 668 186', '2016-12-10 20:00:00', 1, 'info@kinomeetingpoint.ba', 1, 0, 0),
