(2144, 'Divlje meso', 'Wild meat', 100, 'divlje1701', 'divlje1701en', '<p>Divlje meso\r\n</p><p>\r\nPriča je to o propasti, nesreći jedne porodice koja je, kao metafora društva na Balkanu, zapela u međuprostoru između prošlosti koja nikako da prođe i budućnosti koja nikako da dođe. Sukob tradicionalnog, morala koji gubi svoje uporište, krovova predodređenih za rušenje i novih ambicija kojima pojedinci na različite načine pokušavaju opravdati vlastitu egzistenciju, otkriti arhitekturu novog poretka, može završiti samo tragično - jer bujanje bolesti društva uvjetovano okolnostima, bujanje tog tumora nazvanog divlje meso, zatvara sve perspektive. </p>\r\n', '<p>Wild meat\r\n</p><p>\r\nIt is a story about the collapse accident of a family, as a metaphor for society in the Balkans, got stuck in the gap between a past that will not go away and the future that never comes. Conflict of traditional morality loses its footing, roofs destined for demolition and new ambitions which individuals in different ways trying to justify their own existence, to discover the architecture of a new order, can only end in tragedy - because the proliferation of diseases of society conditioned by the circumstances, this proliferation of tumor called wild meat, closes all perspectives. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 226 431', '2017-01-17 19:30:00', 3, 'info@nps.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(2145, 'Latin Sounds', 'Latin Sounds', 1644, 'latin0901', 'latin0901en', '<p>Latin Sounds\r\n</p><p>\r\nKoncept AQUARIUS SARAJEVO pokrenut je davne 1999. na Grbavici tik uz stadion (zgrada LORIS) u želji prezentiranja stečenog ugostiteljskog znanja te iskustva kako u predratnom Sarajevu tako i u inostranstvu. Nakon prvih 6 godina rada,2005. AQUARIUS seli u naselje Šoping u veći i ekskluzivniji prostor u kojem se i sada nalazi. U vječitoj želji za razvojem i profesonalnim usavršavanjem 2007. nastaje firma ZARMED d.o.o. koja se svojim kvalitetom i konstantnim poslovnim napredovanjem, Sarajlijama i gostima Grada, uspijeva nametnuti kao respektabilna firma za ugostiteljstvo i usluge. </p>\r\n', '<p>Latin Sounds\r\n</p><p>\r\nThe concept of Aquarius SARAJEVO was launched back in 1999 in Grbavica next to the stadium (building LORIS) in an effort to present the acquired knowledge and experience of catering to the pre-war Sarajevo and abroad. After the first 6 years of operation, the 2005th Aquarius moves to the village shopping in larger and more exclusive area in which it is situated now. In the eternal desire to develop and 2007. This professional training company formed armed Ltd. that their quality and constant business advancement, the people of Sarajevo and guests of the city, manages to impose such a respectable company for catering and services.</p>\r\n', '', '+387 61 210 788', '2017-01-09 20:00:00', 4, 'aquariussarajevo@gmail.com', 1, 0, 1),
