(2233, 'SKRIVENA LJEPOTA', 'Collateral Beauty', 1145, 'sklje', 'skljeen', '<p>Kada uspješnog njujorškog marketinškog stručnjaka (Will Smith) zadesi velika tragedija, on se u potpunosti povlaći iz svoga dotadašnjeg života, a njegovi kolege smisle plan kako da se suoči sa tugom koju osjeća. Osim Willa Smitha u filmu se još pojavljuju Eward Norton , Keira Knightley Michael Pena, Naomie Harris, Jacob Latimore te dobitnice nagrade Oscar Kate Winslet i Helen Mirren...<br></p>', '<p>When a successful New York advertising executive suffers a great tragedy, he retreats from life. While his concerned friends try desperately to reconnect with him, he seeks answers from the universe by writing letters to Love, Time and Death. But it''s not until his notes bring unexpected personal responses that he begins to understand how these constants interlock in a life fully lived, and how even the deepest loss can reveal moments of meaning and beauty.<br></p>', '/look/events/7899_colar.jpg', '+387 33 567 288', '2017-01-06 18:50:00', 1, 'info@cinemacity.ba', 1, 0, 0),
