(2247, 'LA LA LAND', 'LA LA LAND', 1145, 'lala', 'lalaen', '<p>Riječ je o iščekivanom filmu za Oscara nominiranog redatelja Damiena Chazellea, poznatog po sjajnom i hvaljenom filmu Whiplash...<br><br>U filmu Gosling igra jazz glazbenika koji se zaljubljuje u glumicu u usponu (Emma Stone), nakon čega uslijedi prava ljubavna romansa sa zapletom. Radnja filma smještena je u Los Angeles s naglaskom na atmosferu zlatne ere Hollywooda koja pršti romantikom kakva se ne viđa svaki dan...<br></p>', '<p>Mia, an aspiring actress, serves lattes to movie stars in between auditions and Sebastian, a jazz musician, scrapes by playing cocktail party gigs in dingy bars, but as success mounts they are faced with decisions that begin to fray the fragile fabric of their love affair, and the dreams they worked so hard to maintain in each other threaten to rip them apart.<br></p>', '/look/events/2365_lala.jpg', '+387 33 567 288', '2017-01-06 17:50:00', 1, 'info@cinemacity.ba', 1, 0, 0) ;
