(2304, 'Zabranjeno pušenje', 'Zabranjeno pušenje', 1487, 'zabranjeno2101', 'zabranjeno2101en', '<p>Zabranjeno pušenje\n</p><p>\nZabranjeno pušenje u Coloseum Areni, bend iz Sarajeva pred domaćom publikom za sve generacije! Dođite da zapjevamo brojne hitove. Dobro došli! </p>\n', '<p>Zabranjeno pušenje\n</p><p>\nZabranjeno pušenje in Coloseum Arena, band from Sarajevo in front of  a home crowd for all generations! Come to sing numerous hits with us: ,Anarhija all over Baščaršija, Šeki is on the road again, Zenica Blues. Welcome! </p>\n', '', '+387 33 250 860', '2017-01-21 22:00:00', 4, 'marketing@coloseum-club.com', 1, 0, 1),
(2305, 'Skroz - Svirka uživo', 'Skroz - Live', 5290, 'skroz1401', 'skroz1401en', '<p>Skroz - Svirka uživo\r\n</p><p>\r\nStudentski klub bivših, sadašnjih i budućih studenata kao i onih koji žele da svoje slobodno vrijeme provedu upotpunjeno, radi na principu okupljanja i kohezije različitih generacija. Generacija onih malo starijih koji se sjećaju Kuk-a u jednom pozitivnom svjetlu koji je bio kultno središte okupljanja u Sarajevu, te u kojem su se dešavali različiti kulturno-zabavni programi, ali kao i onih mlađih kojima ćemo ponuditi dugačiji program za razliku od onog kojeg trenutno imamo u gradu. Trudit ćemo se da ambijent bude spoj mladosti i iskustva kroz različite vidove druženja, te da potiče i kreira pozitivnu akademsku misao kao što i sam naziv Studentski klub KUK govori. </p>\r\n', '<p>Skroz - Live\r\n</p><p>\r\nStudent club of former, current and future students, as well as those who want to spend their free time complemented, works on the principle of gathering and cohesion of different generations. The generation of those little older who remember Kuk in a positive light, which was the center of a cult gathering in Sarajevo  and which took place in various cultural programs, or as well as those under which we offer a slightly different program than the one which we currently have in the city. We strive to that environment is a combination of youth and experience through various forms of socializing, and to stimulate and create a positive academic thought as the name Student club KUK says. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 62 500 777', '2017-01-14 21:00:00', 4, '', 1, 0, 1),
(2306, 'Mujo, Suljo i Fata u društvu spektakla', 'Mujo, Suljo, and Fata in the society of the spectacle', 100, 'mujo1901', 'mujo1901en', '<p>Mujo, Suljo i Fata u društvu spektakla\r\n</p><p>\r\nU predstavi Mujo, Suljo i Fata u društvu spektakla pokušali smo da rastumačimo zašto smo tu gdje jesmo? A to mjesto gdje jesmo je ovo: najsiromašnija i najzaostalija zemlja u Evropi. Ova predstava je politička komedija. To je teatar u tradiciji Piscatora, rusko umjetničke avangarde, Brechta, Wilsona i avangardnog filma. Filozofski diskurs u predstavi se nastavlja na djelo Društvo spektakla Guya Deborda. </p>\r\n', '<p>Mujo, Suljo, and Fata in the society of the spectacle\r\n</p><p>\r\nAt present Mujo, Suljo, and Fata in the society of spectacle, we tried to make sense why we are where we are? A place where we are is this: the poorest and most backward country in Europe. This play is a political comedy. The theater is in the tradition of Piscator, Russian artistic avant-garde, Brecht, Wilson and avant-garde film. Philosophical discourse in the play continues to work Society of the Spectacle Guy Debord. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 226 431', '2017-01-19 19:30:00', 3, 'info@nps.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(2307, 'Zmaj od Bosne', 'Zmaj od Bosne', 100, 'zmaj2101', 'zmaj2101en', '<p>Zmaj od Bosne\r\n</p><p>\r\nNarodno pozorište Sarajevo osnovano je 17. 11. 1919. godine, a svečani čin otvaranja, u novembru 1921. godine, pripao je Branislavu Nušiću, tadašnjem načelniku Umjetničkog odjeljenja Ministarstva prosvjete. Tri večeri zaredom izvođeni su muzičko-dramski programi i tako je ozvaničen početak rada kuće. U počecima svog postojanja Narodno pozorište Sarajevo je djelovalo, isključivo, kao dramski teatar. Od 1946. Narodno pozorište dobiva i muzičke segmente djelovanja, pa će tako bogatoj povijesti našeg teatra izuzetno pridonijeti Opera, odnosno Balet. Narodno pozorište Sarajevo je centralna teatarska kuća države BiH i ono je svojim umjetničkim rezultatima, radom generacija umjetnika, a posebno načinom organizacije (tri ansambla Opera, Drama i Balet), veoma važan element teatarskog i uopće duhovnog života u BiH. U toku svog preko 90 godina dugog djelovanja Narodno pozorište Sarajevo odigralo je ogroman broj dramskih, baletnih i opernih predstava po cijeloj Bosni i Hercegovini, ali i u inozemstvu. </p>\r\n', '<p>Zmaj od Bosne\r\n</p><p>\r\nSarajevo National Theatre was founded 17. 11. 1919, a solemn opening, in November 1921, went to Branislav Nušić, then head of the Art Department of the Ministry of Education. Three nights in a row, the music and drama programs, and also marked the start of the house. In the beginning of its existence, Sarajevo National Theatre is operated solely as a drama theater. Since 1946, the National Theatre and gets musical segments of action, and so will the rich history of our theater extremely contribute Opera or Ballet. Sarajevo National Theatre, the central theater house State and what is its artistic results, the work of generations of artists, especially the type of organization (three ensembles Opera, Drama and Ballet), a very important element of theater and even spiritual life in BiH. During his more than 90 years long-acting Sarajevo National Theatre played a huge number of theater, ballet and opera performances throughout Bosnia and Herzegovina, but also abroad. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 226 431', '2017-01-21 19:30:00', 3, 'info@nps.ba', 1, 0, 1),
