(2311, 'Otkrivanje žene', 'Discovering woman', 100, 'zene2801', 'zene2801en', '<p>Otkrivanje žene\r\n</p><p>\r\nOtkrivanje žene je dramski tekst Harisa Pašovića, suvremenog pisca i redatelja koji na neuobičajen i sistematičan način primjećuje i analizira pojave u našem društvu. Sam dramski tekst je nastajao u toku procesa postavljanja predstave. Otkrivanje žene razmatra egzistenciju žene na Balkanu kroz vijekove. </p>\r\n', '<p>Discovering woman\r\n</p><p>\r\nDiscovering Woman is a dramatic text by Haris, contemporary writer and director who in an unusual and systematically observes and analyzes phenomena in our society. Dramatic piece was created in the process of setting performances. Discovering Woman is considering existence of a woman in the Balkans over the centuries. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 226 431', '2017-01-28 19:30:00', 3, 'info@nps.ba', 1, 0, 1),
