(2323, 'Koncert ptica', 'Concert bird', 305, 'ptica2001', 'ptica2001en', '<p>Koncert ptica\r\n</p><p>\r\nTekst je napisan kao svojevrsna parodija kojom autor na jedan vrlo rafiniran način ismijava ljudsku sujetu, želju za vlašću, kao i samu srž naše ljudskosti, koja, ogoljena i razotkrivena, ostaje isprazna, tašta i okrenuta sebi. </p>\r\n', '<p>Concert bird\r\n</p><p>\r\nThe text is written as a parody which the author in a very refined way of making fun of human vanity, the desire for power, as well as the very core of our humanity, which, stripped and exposed, remains worthless, vain and turned itself. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 550 475', '2017-01-20 20:00:00', 3, 'info@kamerniteatar55.ba', 1, 0, 1),
