(2357, '4 Kralja', '4 Kings', 505, 'kralja2501', 'kralja2501en', '<p>4 Kralja\r\n</p><p>\r\nZbog nemogućnosti da se nosi s roditeljima koji se stalno svađaju, Alex donosi radikalnu odluku. Slijedeći dan se nalazi u Ambulanti za hitne slučajeve Psihijatrijske klinike za mlade. Tamo upoznaje: Laru, iz akademske porodice koja je ovisnica o drogama, Fedju, koju su maltretirali u školi, te Timu, koji je upravo otpušten iz Zatvorenog odjeljenja. U skrbi mladog psihijatra Dr. Wolffa provode nezaboravan Božić i shvate koliko njihovo ludilo može izgledati drugačije ako se posmatra iz druge perspektive. </p>\r\n', '<p>4 Kings\r\n</p><p>\r\nUnable to cope with parents who are constantly arguing, Alex brings a radical decision. The next day he finds himself in the Outpatient Emergency Ward of the Psychiatric Clinic for young people. There he meets: Lara, a drug addict from a family of academicians, Fedja, who was bullied at school, and Timo, who was just released from the Security Ward. In the care of a young psychiatrist Dr. Wolff, they spend an unforgettable Christmas and realize how their madness may look different when viewed from another perspective. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 668 186', '2017-01-25 20:00:00', 1, 'info@kinomeetingpoint.ba', 1, 0, 0),
(2358, 'Nešad Selman', 'Nešad Selman', 1632, 'nesad1801', 'nesad1801en', '<p>Nešad Selman\r\n</p><p>\r\nHistorija, tradicija i kvalitet na jednom mjestu, najbolje opisuju jedinstveni ugostiteljski objekat u Sarajevu – Pivnicu HS. Nalazi se u Centru Sarajeva, u dijelu Starog Grada na Bistriku, samo nekoliko metara od Sarajevske pivare, u zgradi koja je zaštićeni historijski objekt. Pored Pivnice HS nalazi se jedini muzej pivarstva u BiH. </p>\r\n', '<p>Nešad Selman\r\n</p><p>\r\nHistory, tradition and quality in one place, best describe the unique restaurant in Sarajevo - Pub HS. It is located in the center of Sarajevo, in part of the Old City in Bistrik, just a few meters from Sarajevo Brewery, in a building that is a protected historic building. In addition to the pub HS is the only brewery museum in BiH. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 239 740', '2017-01-18 21:00:00', 4, 'pivnica.hs@pivara.ba', 1, 0, 1),
