(2419, 'Friday''s Salsa Night', 'Friday''s Salsa Night', 5290, 'salsa1301', 'salsa1301en', '<p>Friday''s Salsa Night\r\n</p><p>\r\nStudentski klub bivših, sadašnjih i budućih studenata kao i onih koji žele da svoje slobodno vrijeme provedu upotpunjeno, radi na principu okupljanja i kohezije različitih generacija. Generacija onih malo starijih koji se sjećaju Kuk-a u jednom pozitivnom svjetlu koji je bio kultno središte okupljanja u Sarajevu, te u kojem su se dešavali različiti kulturno-zabavni programi, ali kao i onih mlađih kojima ćemo ponuditi dugačiji program za razliku od onog kojeg trenutno imamo u gradu. Trudit ćemo se da ambijent bude spoj mladosti i iskustva kroz različite vidove druženja, te da potiče i kreira pozitivnu akademsku misao kao što i sam naziv Studentski klub KUK govori. </p>\r\n', '<p>Friday''s Salsa Night\r\n</p><p>\r\nStudent club of former, current and future students, as well as those who want to spend their free time complemented, works on the principle of gathering and cohesion of different generations. The generation of those little older who remember Kuk in a positive light, which was the center of a cult gathering in Sarajevo  and which took place in various cultural programs, or as well as those under which we offer a slightly different program than the one which we currently have in the city. We strive to that environment is a combination of youth and experience through various forms of socializing, and to stimulate and create a positive academic thought as the name Student club KUK says.  </p>\r\n', '', '+387 62 500 777', '2017-01-13 21:00:00', 4, '', 1, 0, 1),
(2421, 'Nolimitnow', 'Nolimitnow', 393, 'nolimitnow2801', 'nolimitnow2801en', '<p>Nolimitnow\n</p><p>\nClub Cinemas Sloga pruža ugodnu zabavu uz raznovrstan program: muzika uživo, klubski koncerti, tematske i salsa večeri, te muziku uz resident DJ-a.Nemojte se iznenaditi ukoliko u našem Club-u naiđete na događaje koje još uvijek niste imali priliku vidjeti u našem gradu.\nTrudimo se da svaki vaš izlazak bude ugodan i zabavan. </p>\n', '<p>Nolimitnow\n</p><p>\nClub Cinemas Sloga provides pleasant entertainment with a varied program: live music, club concerts, thematic and salsa nights, and music with resident DJ.Do not be surprised if in our Club you encounter events that have not yet experienced in our city.\nWe try to make your every night out enjoyable and fun. </p>\n', '', '+387 33 218 811', '2017-01-28 23:00:00', 4, 'info@cinemas.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(2424, 'Saturday LIVE ProRocks', 'Saturday LIVE ProRocks', 2960, 'saturday1401', 'saturday1401en', '<p>Saturday LIVE ProRocks\r\n</p><p>\r\nU PUB, sa svojim ukrasnim unutrašnjost sastanak na visokom nivou pub standardima u svijetu, je mjesto za rock & roll ljubitelje muzike i ljubitelje žive svirke da se okupe, nudeći im širok spektar alkoholnih i bezalkoholnih pića / pića ... DOBRODOŠLI!</p>\r\n\r\n', '<p>Saturday LIVE ProRocks\r\n</p><p>\r\nThe PUB, with its decorative interior meeting high level pub standards worldwide, is a place for rock&roll music lovers and live gigs fans to gather, offering them a wide range of alcoholic and non-alcoholic drinks/beverages... WELCOME!.</p>\r\n', '', '+387 62 152 152', '2017-01-14 23:00:00', 4, '', 0, 0, 1),
