(2442, 'Ružno pače', 'Ugly duckling', 100, 'ruzno0802', 'ruzno0802en', '<p>Ružno pače\r\n</p><p>\r\nNaša predstava za djecu Ružno pače rađena je prema jednoj od najljepših bajki Hansa C. Andersona. Priča o pačetu koje svi odbacuju jer je drugačije i kojem se ismijavaju, a koje posataje fantastičan labud koji zasjeni sve – prijča je o tome da nema predaje, da svačija osobnost može doći do izražaja, da biti drugačiji ne znači biti slabiji od drugih. To je priča koje svako dijete treba da zna.</p>\r\n', '<p>Ugly duckling\r\n</p><p>\r\nOur performances for children, The Ugly Duckling was done to one of the most beautiful fairy tales of Hans C. Anderson. The story of the duckling that all discarded because it is different and that is ridiculed, and it became fantastic swan that overshadowed all - story is that no surrender to everyone''s personality can be revealed to be different does not mean being weaker than the other. It''s a story that every child needs to know.</p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 226 431', '2017-02-08 12:00:00', 3, 'info@nps.ba', 1, 0, 1),
