(2457, 'Queen Real Tribute', 'Queen Real Tribute', 393, 'queen0303 ', 'queen0303en', '<p>Queen Real Tribute\r\n</p><p>\r\nQueen Real Tribute je najveći evropski Queen tribute projekat, bend koji je obišao pola svijeta (samo u Brazilu preko 70 koncerata),\r\nnastupao na mnogim velikim festivalima i Queen konvencijama.\r\nOsim odlične svirke i energije, bend krase i sjajni kostimi, poput\r\nonih koji se nosili originalni članovi velikog Queen-a. Gitarista\r\nsvira istu gitaru i svira metalnim novcem, baš kao i Brian May, da bi dobio originalnu boju zvuka na gitari, a pjevač benda ima potpuno\r\nistu boju glasa kao Freddy. </p>\r\n', '<p>Queen Real Tribute\r\n</p><p>\r\nQueen Real Tribute is Europe''s biggest Queen tribute project, a band that is halfway around the world (only in Brazil over 70 concerts)\r\nperformed at many major festivals and Queen conventions.\r\nIn addition to excellent performances and energy, the band decorated with bright costumes, such as\r\nthose worn by the original members of the great Queen''s. guitarist\r\nplaying the same guitar and playing coins, just like Brian May, in order to obtain the original tone of the guitar, a singer of the band has completely\r\nthe same tone of voice as Freddy. </p>\r\n', '', '+387 33 218 811', '2017-03-03 20:00:00', 4, 'info@cinemas.ba', 1, 0, 1),
(2458, 'Sajsi MC DJ Bko', 'Sajsi MC DJ Bko', 393, 'sajsi1703', 'sajsi1703en', '<p>Sajsi MC DJ Bko \n</p><p>\nSajsi MC je pseudonim za Ivanu Rašić, koja od 2011. surađuje i nastupa sa DJ BKO-om te neizostavnom Tijanom Rasić aka MC Schweca Rispek koja je od samih početaka itekako prisutna. </p>\n', '<p>Sajsi MC DJ Bko \n</p><p>\nSsjsi MC is a pseudonym for John Rasic, who from 2011 collaborates and performs with DJ BKO-player and an indispensable Tijana Rasic aka MC Schweca Rispek that from the very beginning is very much present. </p>\n', '', '+387 33 218 811', '2017-03-17 20:00:10', 4, 'info@cinemas.ba', 1, 0, 1),
